Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:03.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, well this is it.\N{\rChinese}好的，事情就到此为止。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:07.08,English,,0,0,0,,The end of the journey, the final class.\N{\rChinese}旅程的终点，最终的课堂。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:11.00,English,,0,0,0,,So we've done a lot this year, right?\N{\rChinese}今年我们做了不少事，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:15.14,English,,0,0,0,,Last semester we did the great books, the Iliad,\N{\rChinese}上学期我们读了伟大的书，伊利亚特，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.80,English,,0,0,0,,the Odyssey, the Bible,\N{\rChinese}奥德赛，圣经，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.10,English,,0,0,0,,Republic, Divine Comedy.\N{\rChinese}共和国，神曲。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.62,English,,0,0,0,,This semester we did how screwed up the world is, right?\N{\rChinese}本学期我们讨论了世界到底有多乱，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.68,English,,0,0,0,,The world is hopeless. We're all going to die.\N{\rChinese}世界一片混乱。我们都要死了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:33.12,English,,0,0,0,,And in this final class,\N{\rChinese}在这最后一堂课里，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:36.50,English,,0,0,0,,I want this class to be about hope.\N{\rChinese}我想让这堂课充满希望。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:41.76,English,,0,0,0,,And I want to show you the future.\N{\rChinese}我想给你们展示未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:47.28,English,,0,0,0,,And the argument I want to leave you with,\N{\rChinese}我想留给你们的论点是，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:50.70,English,,0,0,0,,the thing that I want you to remember is that,\N{\rChinese}我想让你记住的事是，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.44,English,,0,0,0,,remember Dante in Divine Comedy said that\N{\rChinese}记得但丁在《神曲》中说过，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.66,English,,0,0,0,,the future, the future is the future.\N{\rChinese}未来，未来就是未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.50,English,,0,0,0,,And the future is the future. And the future is the future. And the future is the future. And the future is the future. And the future is the future. And the future is not what happens to you.\N{\rChinese}未来就是未来。未来就是未来。未来就是未来。未来就是未来。未来就是未来。未来不是你所经历的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:01.92,English,,0,0,0,,It's not something that you wait for.\N{\rChinese}它不是你等待的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:05.28,English,,0,0,0,,The future is what you imagine\N{\rChinese}未来是你想象的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:08.06,English,,0,0,0,,and fight for.\N{\rChinese}并为之而战。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.88,English,,0,0,0,,The future is what you make happen.\N{\rChinese}未来是你创造的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:15.06,English,,0,0,0,,There is a God, but\N{\rChinese}有一位神，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:17.72,English,,0,0,0,,God gave us the ability to imagine\N{\rChinese}上帝赐给我们想象的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.06,English,,0,0,0,,and the capacity to love.\N{\rChinese}以及爱的能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.50,English,,0,0,0,,And it's these two things that will guide us\N{\rChinese}这两件事将指引我们。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.64,English,,0,0,0,,and enable us to build a better world.\N{\rChinese}并使我们能构建更好的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:31.42,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So that's the message I want to give to you today.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是我今天想给你们的消息。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:33.92,English,,0,0,0,,The future is what we imagine.\N{\rChinese}未来是我们想象的结果。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:38.34,English,,0,0,0,,Not what we have to put up with.\N{\rChinese}不是我们必须忍受的事物。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:42.16,English,,0,0,0,,So if we don't like the future, if we don't like the way we live our lives,\N{\rChinese}如果我们不喜欢未来，如果我们不喜欢我们生活的方式，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.96,English,,0,0,0,,then we can change that with our imagination.\N{\rChinese}那么我们可以用想象去改变它。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.28,English,,0,0,0,,And today I want to show you how.\N{\rChinese}今天我想给你们演示如何做。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:51.62,English,,0,0,0,,So just to summarize what we did this semester.\N{\rChinese}简而言之，我们本学期做了什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:57.26,English,,0,0,0,,Together we analyzed the world.\N{\rChinese}我们一起分析了世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.46,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.30,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future. But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.22,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.06,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:14.86,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future. But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:19.02,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future. But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:22.04,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.60,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.62,English,,0,0,0,,But what are some of the other two things you can learn about the future.\N{\rChinese}那还有另外两件你可以了解未来的事物是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:31.00,English,,0,0,0,,millions and billions of people.\N{\rChinese}数以百万计的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:32.98,English,,0,0,0,,And because of climate change,\N{\rChinese}因为气候变化，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:37.36,English,,0,0,0,,our world will eventually collapse at some point, okay?\N{\rChinese}我们的世界最终会在某个时点崩溃，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:41.36,English,,0,0,0,,So this is an extremely hopeless,\N{\rChinese}于是这是一幅极其无望的，极其黯淡而黑暗的世界图景。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.40,English,,0,0,0,,extremely bleak and dark picture of the world.\N{\rChinese}但记住，黑暗之处亦有光明。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:50.94,English,,0,0,0,,But remember, where there is darkness, there can also be light.\N{\rChinese}But remember, where there is darkness, there can also be light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:54.66,English,,0,0,0,,So in this final class, I want to show you\N{\rChinese}于是在这最后一课，我想给你们展示一些希望和光明，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.78,English,,0,0,0,,some hope and some light, okay?\N{\rChinese}于是这就是我们所说的心理历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.96,English,,0,0,0,,So this is what we call psychohistory.\N{\rChinese}So this is what wecall psychohistory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.50,English,,0,0,0,,And psychohistory is the idea\N{\rChinese}而心理历史就是这样一个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:09.20,English,,0,0,0,,that the future can be predicted.\N{\rChinese}未来可以被预测。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:13.12,English,,0,0,0,,And if it can be predicted, then it can be controlled\N{\rChinese}如果能预测，未来就能被掌控。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.78,English,,0,0,0,,and harnessed for the betterment of humanity, okay?\N{\rChinese}并为人类的更好而被利用，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:21.58,English,,0,0,0,,So where does this idea come from, psychohistory?\N{\rChinese}那么这个想法从哪里来，心理历史？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.82,English,,0,0,0,,In the 1950s,\N{\rChinese}在1950年代，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:28.32,English,,0,0,0,,there was an American science fiction writer named Isaac Asimov.\N{\rChinese}有一位美国科幻作家叫艾萨克·阿西莫夫。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.66,English,,0,0,0,,And he's probably\N{\rChinese}他大概是……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.14,English,,0,0,0,,the most famous science fiction writer, okay?\N{\rChinese}他是最著名的科幻作家，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:37.20,English,,0,0,0,,If you happen to read science fiction, he's really famous.\N{\rChinese}如果你碰巧读过科幻，他真是大名鼎鼎。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.68,English,,0,0,0,,And he wrote a series called Foundation.\N{\rChinese}他写了一系列叫《基地》的书。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:48.76,English,,0,0,0,,And I think there's a TV series now based on Foundation books.\N{\rChinese}我觉得现在有一部基于《基地》书的电视剧。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.84,English,,0,0,0,,It's terrible, but you can have a look at it.\N{\rChinese}太糟了，但你可以看看。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:56.22,English,,0,0,0,,And in the Foundation books, he introduces the idea of psychohistory.\N{\rChinese}在《基地》书里，他提出了心理史的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:04:00.84,English,,0,0,0,,And so this book is set in the future,\N{\rChinese}于是这本书的背景设在未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.28,English,,0,0,0,,like a million years from now, where there is a galactic empire.\N{\rChinese}大约一百万年后，出现了一个银河帝国。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.28,English,,0,0,0,,So humanity has colonized the entire Milky Way.\N{\rChinese}于是人类已把整个银河系殖民化。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.08,English,,0,0,0,,There are billions of planets.\N{\rChinese}星系中有数十亿颗行星。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.82,English,,0,0,0,,And there's an empire that\N{\rChinese}还有一个帝国，把银河系带入和平。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:18.80,English,,0,0,0,,brings peace to this Milky Way.\N{\rChinese}但所有帝国都必然崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.48,English,,0,0,0,,But with all empires, it has to collapse.\N{\rChinese}But with all empires, it has to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:27.10,English,,0,0,0,,And this will lead to 30,000 years of war,\N{\rChinese}于是会出现三万年的战争、暴力与野蛮。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:32.64,English,,0,0,0,,violence, barbarity. But\N{\rChinese}但随后，基础提出了一门新科学——心理史学。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:38.10,English,,0,0,0,,the foundation proposes a new science called psychohistory.\N{\rChinese}the foundation proposes a newscience called psychohistory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:41.88,English,,0,0,0,,Which is to mathematically map out\N{\rChinese}哪是把人类行为在一百万年间用数学映射出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:46.06,English,,0,0,0,,human behavior over the course of a million years.\N{\rChinese}人类行为在一百万年间用数学映射出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.40,English,,0,0,0,,But if you do that, what you discover is\N{\rChinese}人类行为在一百万年间用数学映射出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:53.20,English,,0,0,0,,that there are certain patterns to human society.\N{\rChinese}那表明人类社会存在某些模式。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.92,English,,0,0,0,,But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain standards to human society. But the way you discover is that there are certain Okay?\N{\rChinese}但你发现的方式是人类社会存在某些标准。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,And if that's the case, then you can predict the future.\N{\rChinese}如果是这样，你就能预测未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.60,English,,0,0,0,,If you can do that, then\N{\rChinese}如果你能做到这一点，就能操纵事件进程，创造更好的未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:05.96,English,,0,0,0,,you can manipulate the course of events to make a better future.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是他所说的“心理历史”。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:09.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So this is what he called psychohistory.\N{\rChinese}Okay? So this is what he called psychohistory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.18,English,,0,0,0,,And it's a science fiction concept.\N{\rChinese}它是科幻概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:16.26,English,,0,0,0,,And a lot of people have been trying to make it into reality.\N{\rChinese}许多人已尝试把它变成现实。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:22.32,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So there's this very prominent historian.\N{\rChinese}于是出现了这位极具影响力的历史学家。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.54,English,,0,0,0,,His name is Peter Turkin.\N{\rChinese}他的名字是彼得·图尔金。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:30.90,English,,0,0,0,,And he's one of the founders of something called Clio Dynamics.\N{\rChinese}他是被称为克利奥动力学的某个组织的创始人之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.18,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.44,English,,0,0,0,,Clio is the goddess of history.\N{\rChinese}克利奥是历史女神。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.52,English,,0,0,0,,Dynamics just means movement.\N{\rChinese}动态只是指运动。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.46,English,,0,0,0,,basically Clio Dynamics is trying to figure\N{\rChinese}基本上，克利奥动力学正试图弄清数学历史的运动规律。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:47.20,English,,0,0,0,,out the mathematical movement of the mathematical history.\N{\rChinese}他正试图把历史建模成一个数学模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:51.66,English,,0,0,0,,He's trying to create history as a mathematical model.\N{\rChinese}He's trying to create history as a mathematical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.16,English,,0,0,0,,And when he did that, there's certain interesting trends\N{\rChinese}当他这么做时，出现了一些有趣的趋势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.88,English,,0,0,0,,and patterns that he discovered.\N{\rChinese}以及他发现的模式。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.40,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And one idea that\N{\rChinese}好的吗？还有一个想法是。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.32,English,,0,0,0,,he discovered is something called the\N{\rChinese}他发现的东西叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:08.86,English,,0,0,0,,overproduction of\N{\rChinese}过度生产的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.20,English,,0,0,0,,the elites.\N{\rChinese}精英
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.22,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Overproduction of the elite.\N{\rChinese}好的？精英过度生产。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.68,English,,0,0,0,,And this concept explains why.\N{\rChinese}这个概念解释了原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.32,English,,0,0,0,,So this concept explains why societies collapse. Now, traditionally,\N{\rChinese}所以这个概念解释了社会崩溃的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.46,English,,0,0,0,,we've understood the collapse of societies as having to\N{\rChinese}我们已经把社会崩溃理解为可能与过多债务、过大不平等或气候变迁或战争有关。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:30.20,English,,0,0,0,,do with maybe like too much debt or too much inequality or maybe climate change or war.\N{\rChinese}对吗？彼得·图尔金指出的，...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.54,English,,0,0,0,,Right? What Peter Turkin points out, and\N{\rChinese}Right? What Peter Turkin points out, and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:34.76,English,,0,0,0,,it's a really interesting idea,\N{\rChinese}这真是个很有趣的想法，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:37.82,English,,0,0,0,,is the reason why societies collapse in the\N{\rChinese}是导致社会崩溃的原因，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:41.16,English,,0,0,0,,end is you have too many elites.\N{\rChinese}最终是因为你有太多精英。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.88,English,,0,0,0,,All right? So let me explain the concept.\N{\rChinese}好的！那我来解释一下这个概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.78,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So.\N{\rChinese}好的。那。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:49.24,English,,0,0,0,,So.! Society has many elites.\N{\rChinese}于是！社会拥有许多精英。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.78,English,,0,0,0,,Right? You have people like Jack Ma.\N{\rChinese}对吧？你有像马云那样的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.70,English,,0,0,0,,Right? You have people like Zhou Xun, Zhao Wei.\N{\rChinese}对吧？你有像周迅、赵伟那样的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:07:00.40,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Movie stars. You have famous military generals.\N{\rChinese}对吧？电影明星。你有著名的军队将领。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So\N{\rChinese}好的？那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.86,English,,0,0,0,,over time, elites become more and more numerous.\N{\rChinese}随着时间推移，精英越来越多。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:11.10,English,,0,0,0,,Right? The number of wealthy people go up.\N{\rChinese}对吧？富裕的人数增多。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.60,English,,0,0,0,,The number of famous people go up.\N{\rChinese}名人数量增多。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.66,English,,0,0,0,,The number of uneducated people go up.\N{\rChinese}未受教育者数量增多。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.08,English,,0,0,0,,The number of entrepreneurs go up. Okay?\N{\rChinese}创业者数量增多。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.80,English,,0,0,0,,The problem, though,\N{\rChinese}问题是，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.94,English,,0,0,0,,is they all want power.\N{\rChinese}他们都想要权力。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.42,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Now, wealth and\N{\rChinese}对吧？现在，财富和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:31.40,English,,0,0,0,,fame are all infinite resources.\N{\rChinese}名气是所有无限资源。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.64,English,,0,0,0,,Right? But\N{\rChinese}对吧？但
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.82,English,,0,0,0,,power will always be a finite resource.\N{\rChinese}权力永远是有限资源。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:42.14,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's what we call a zero -sum game.\N{\rChinese}实际上，这就是我们所说的零和游戏。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.24,English,,0,0,0,,So, for example, in this classroom, there can only be one teacher.\N{\rChinese}例如，在这个教室里，最多只能有一位老师。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.14,English,,0,0,0,,Right? If we're all teachers, there's no teacher.\N{\rChinese}对吧？如果我们都是老师，那就没有老师。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:55.56,English,,0,0,0,,So in society, there can only be a few powerful people.\N{\rChinese}于是，在社会中，最多只有少数强者。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:58.02,English,,0,0,0,,If everyone has the power, no one has any power.\N{\rChinese}若人人皆有权力，便无一人有权力。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.92,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So what happens over time is that\N{\rChinese}好了？于是随着时间的推移，发生了……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:04.22,English,,0,0,0,,all these people who\N{\rChinese}所有这些人都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:08.22,English,,0,0,0,,believe they should have power struggle for power.\N{\rChinese}认为自己应该拥有权力，争夺权力。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.42,English,,0,0,0,,And because there are too many of them,\N{\rChinese}而且因为他们太多，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:15.62,English,,0,0,0,,this internal struggle of the elites ultimately leads to social collapse.\N{\rChinese}这场内部精英斗争最终导致社会崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:20.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So the most famous example is in China,\N{\rChinese}好啦？最著名的例子在中国，帝制中国。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:24.52,English,,0,0,0,,in imperial China, where you have the Keju system.\N{\rChinese}在帝制中国，出现了科举制度。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:29.68,English,,0,0,0,,Right? People taking the imperial examinations to become an official.\N{\rChinese}对吧？人们参加科举考试成为官员。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:33.68,English,,0,0,0,,Problem is, you have too many candidates,\N{\rChinese}问题是，候选人太多，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.64,English,,0,0,0,,not enough positions.\N{\rChinese}职位不够。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:40.18,English,,0,0,0,,Right? And guess who ultimately gets upset with society\N{\rChinese}对吧？猜猜谁最终对社会不满并发动革命？是科举考生。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.88,English,,0,0,0,,and leads revolutions? It's the Keju candidates.\N{\rChinese}谁没能当官。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.78,English,,0,0,0,,Who do not become officials.\N{\rChinese}Who do not become officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.96,English,,0,0,0,,And so they become angry.\N{\rChinese}于是他们愤怒起来。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.98,English,,0,0,0,,And they lead revolutions to overthrow society.\N{\rChinese}于是他们发动革命推翻社会。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.82,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So\N{\rChinese}对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.36,English,,0,0,0,,the most classic example of the\N{\rChinese}最经典的例子是洪秀全。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:02.76,English,,0,0,0,,failed Keju candidate is Hong Xiuquan.\N{\rChinese}洪秀全是个考生。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.82,English,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know who he is?\N{\rChinese}你们知道他是谁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.60,English,,0,0,0,,The leader of the Taiping rebellion.\N{\rChinese}太平军的领袖。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.78,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Why did he become a Christian?\N{\rChinese}对吧？他为什么会成为基督徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.48,English,,0,0,0,,Why did he lead the rebellion?\N{\rChinese}他为什么发动太平军？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.22,English,,0,0,0,,Because he failed the Keju.\N{\rChinese}因为他考取了科举。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:19.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So that's the idea of the overproduction of the elite.\N{\rChinese}好吧？这就是精英过度生产的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:25.28,English,,0,0,0,,And he discovered this principle using mathematically modeling of history.\N{\rChinese}他用历史的数学建模发现了这一原理。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.46,English,,0,0,0,,He just compared different societies and\N{\rChinese}他只是比较了不同的社会并
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:32.42,English,,0,0,0,,tried to figure out why they collapsed.\N{\rChinese}尝试弄清它们为何崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.18,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And what he discovered is, well, it's because\N{\rChinese}好的？他发现的结果是，嗯，就是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:40.32,English,,0,0,0,,of the internal struggle among the different elite groups.\N{\rChinese}不同精英团体内部斗争的结果。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.98,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And that's why the Roman Empire collapsed as well.\N{\rChinese}好吧？这也是罗马帝国崩溃的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.16,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? Okay.\N{\rChinese}好吧？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.28,English,,0,0,0,,What I'm proposing to you is that\N{\rChinese}我想给你提个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:53.28,English,,0,0,0,,we can actually go a step further than what Peter Turchin is doing.\N{\rChinese}我们可以比彼得·图尔奇所做的更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.90,English,,0,0,0,,Because we have something called now called AI.\N{\rChinese}因为现在我们有了所谓的人工智能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:10:01.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Artificial intelligence. And\N{\rChinese}好吧？人工智能。和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:07.30,English,,0,0,0,,we can harness the power of AI to create real psychohistory,\N{\rChinese}我们可以利用AI的力量来创造真正的心理历史，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.72,English,,0,0,0,,which is the ability to not just analyze the past,\N{\rChinese}这就是不仅能分析过去的能力，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.72,English,,0,0,0,,but to predict the future.\N{\rChinese}但用来预测未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right.\N{\rChinese}好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.14,English,,0,0,0,,So let's first figure out what AI is.\N{\rChinese}先来搞清楚AI是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.40,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So first I want us to understand what artificial intelligence is.\N{\rChinese}好吧？先让我们弄清楚什么是人工智能。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.98,English,,0,0,0,,Because most of you think you know, but you don't actually know.\N{\rChinese}因为你们大多数人觉得自己知道，但其实并不懂。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So what is AI?\N{\rChinese}好吧？那AI到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.80,English,,0,0,0,,All right. The AI, the technical term,\N{\rChinese}好的。AI，技术术语，是监督式机器学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.86,English,,0,0,0,,is supervised\N{\rChinese}是监督式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:42.60,English,,0,0,0,,machine learning.\N{\rChinese}机器学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's the technical term.\N{\rChinese}好的？那是技术术语。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.82,English,,0,0,0,,AI is the popular term, but\N{\rChinese}AI是大众术语，但
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:54.14,English,,0,0,0,,supervised machine learning is the technical\N{\rChinese}监督式机器学习是技术术语。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.62,English,,0,0,0,,and correct term.\N{\rChinese}以及正确术语。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.08,English,,0,0,0,,Have you guys heard of this term?\N{\rChinese}你们听说过这个术语吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.86,English,,0,0,0,,Supervised machine learning.\N{\rChinese}监督式机器学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:03.10,English,,0,0,0,,Yes or no? Have any of you taken computer science?\N{\rChinese}是或否？你们有人学过计算机科学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.30,English,,0,0,0,,Yes. Okay.\N{\rChinese}是。好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.78,English,,0,0,0,,This is called supervised machine learning.\N{\rChinese}这叫做监督式机器学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So what is this?\N{\rChinese}好的。那么这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:14.00,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So in computer programming,\N{\rChinese}好的。在计算机编程里，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.22,English,,0,0,0,,you're taught to write the algorithm, right?\N{\rChinese}你被教写算法，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:21.26,English,,0,0,0,,And then the input. You put in information, it gives you the output.\N{\rChinese}然后是输入。你放入信息，它给你输出。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:25.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And this is traditionally how computers work.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是传统的计算机工作方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:28.50,English,,0,0,0,,You write the algorithm, the computer program,\N{\rChinese}你写算法，计算机程序。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:32.04,English,,0,0,0,,you put in information, and then there's an output, right?\N{\rChinese}你放入信息，然后得到输出，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:36.84,English,,0,0,0,,For example, the algorithm could be like, you know, A plus B.\N{\rChinese}比如，算法可以是这样，你知道，A 加 B。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So you put in two numbers. Two, two, you get a four.\N{\rChinese}好的？所以你放入两个数字，两个，得到四。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.08,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's how computers work.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是计算机的工作方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.62,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Now, supervised machine learning is\N{\rChinese}对吧？现在，监督式机器学习是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:51.40,English,,0,0,0,,that I will turn the output into the input.\N{\rChinese}我会把输出变成输入。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the reason why I want to do that\N{\rChinese}好的？我想这么做的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.46,English,,0,0,0,,is that as a human being,\N{\rChinese}作为人类，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:03.36,English,,0,0,0,,I myself may not be able to write the best algorithm.\N{\rChinese}我自己可能写不出最优算法。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So\N{\rChinese}好的？那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:11.90,English,,0,0,0,,I want the computer to refine the algorithm for me,\N{\rChinese}我想让电脑为我完善算法，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:16.24,English,,0,0,0,,to optimize it using the output.\N{\rChinese}用输出结果来优化它。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? All right.\N{\rChinese}好的？这样说通吗？好吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.90,English,,0,0,0,,So let's talk about a very specific example.\N{\rChinese}那我们来聊一个非常具体的例子。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.36,English,,0,0,0,,All right? So\N{\rChinese}好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:28.06,English,,0,0,0,,let's look at facial recognition technology.\N{\rChinese}让我们来看看人脸识别技术。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:32.12,English,,0,0,0,,All right? You go to the airport, and you scan,\N{\rChinese}好吧？你去机场，扫描一下，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.92,English,,0,0,0,,and they know who you are.\N{\rChinese}然后他们就知道你是谁。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:38.06,English,,0,0,0,,Right? You go to a supermarket, you scan your face, and you pay.\N{\rChinese}对吧？你去超市，扫描自己的脸，然后付款。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.12,English,,0,0,0,,Right? And you're like, wait, how does that work?\N{\rChinese}对吧？你会想，等一下，这怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So\N{\rChinese}好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:47.56,English,,0,0,0,,how this works is that there's a database,\N{\rChinese}这件事的工作原理是有一个数据库，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:51.30,English,,0,0,0,,okay, about 1 billion people, like everyone in China.\N{\rChinese}好了，大约一亿人，像中国人一样。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.90,English,,0,0,0,,And now what I need to do is figure out\N{\rChinese}现在我需要做的事是弄清楚。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:59.64,English,,0,0,0,,how to differentiate the faces of everyone in China in this database.\N{\rChinese}如何在这个数据库里区分中国人所有人的面孔。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? So what I do is,\N{\rChinese}好？这有道理吗？于是我做的是，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.38,English,,0,0,0,,for the face, I want to figure out how to differentiate the faces of everyone in China.\N{\rChinese}对面孔，我想弄清楚如何区分中国人所有人的面孔。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:09.26,English,,0,0,0,,So I go to the database, I create a mathematical model based on topology.\N{\rChinese}于是我去数据库，基于拓扑创建了一个数学模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.56,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? Topology.\N{\rChinese}好？这有道理吗？拓扑。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:18.98,English,,0,0,0,,So I turn everyone's face into a mathematical model.\N{\rChinese}于是我把每个人的面孔转化成数学模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.22,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Which looks like something like this.\N{\rChinese}好的？看起来像这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:26.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And you're like, I don't know what this is.\N{\rChinese}好的？你会说，我不知道这是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. You don't need to know what this is.\N{\rChinese}好的。你不需要知道这是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.66,English,,0,0,0,,This is like super complicated. Okay?\N{\rChinese}这就像超级复杂。好？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.54,English,,0,0,0,,But all you need to know is that within this model,\N{\rChinese}但你只需要知道的是，在这个模型里，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.02,English,,0,0,0,,there are different equations.\N{\rChinese}有不同的方程。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.66,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So for example,\N{\rChinese}好的？比如说，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:41.26,English,,0,0,0,,this model is trying to analyze the distance between your eyes.\N{\rChinese}这个模型试图分析你眼睛之间的距离。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And how big your nose is.\N{\rChinese}好的？还有你鼻子的大小。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.24,English,,0,0,0,,All right? Does that make sense? All right?\N{\rChinese}好的？那有道理吗？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.04,English,,0,0,0,,And so once I create this mathematical model,\N{\rChinese}于是我一旦创建了这个数学模型，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:56.50,English,,0,0,0,,I am now able to differentiate everyone in\N{\rChinese}我就能把每个人区分出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:00.14,English,,0,0,0,,China. Does that make sense? Okay?\N{\rChinese}中国。那有道理吗？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:03.04,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, this mathematical is so\N{\rChinese}事实上，这个数学模型非常精准，只有我能看见你的眼睛。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.22,English,,0,0,0,,precise that I can only look at your eyes.\N{\rChinese}我现在可以只看你的眼睛。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.78,English,,0,0,0,,And I know who you are. Okay? Because\N{\rChinese}我也知道你是谁。好的？因为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:14.62,English,,0,0,0,,what I'm trying to do is match what your model with the model in the database.\N{\rChinese}我正在做的事是把你的模型与数据库里的模型匹配。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.68,English,,0,0,0,,All right? But\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:21.08,English,,0,0,0,,what's important to remember is that if you're not in this database,\N{\rChinese}要记住的事是，如果你不在这个数据库里，就会被认不出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.46,English,,0,0,0,,you can't be recognized.\N{\rChinese}好的？你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Do you understand? All right.\N{\rChinese}好啦。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:30.48,English,,0,0,0,,Now, what I will show you is how this model is created.\N{\rChinese}现在，我要给你展示这个模型是如何创建的。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.96,English,,0,0,0,,So what happens is this. All right?\N{\rChinese}于是发生的事就是这样。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:38.56,English,,0,0,0,,What I do is I teach the computer how to create this database.\N{\rChinese}我做的是教电脑如何创建这个数据库。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:44.64,English,,0,0,0,,So I have input. I have output. And then\N{\rChinese}于是我有输入，我有输出。然后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:47.42,English,,0,0,0,,what I do is I create a\N{\rChinese}我做的是我创建一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:52.50,English,,0,0,0,,working thesis or a working theory of\N{\rChinese}工作论点或工作理论
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.26,English,,0,0,0,,what this model should look like. Okay?\N{\rChinese}这个模型应该是怎样的。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.80,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? All right?\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:15:00.04,English,,0,0,0,,So it could be like this. All right?\N{\rChinese}它可以是这样的。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:06.14,English,,0,0,0,,And then what I do is I create a working thesis. So what I do is I put faces.\N{\rChinese}于是我做的是我创建一个工作论点。然后我把面孔放进去。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:11.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the output should match what's in the database.\N{\rChinese}好了？输出应该与数据库里的内容匹配。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:16.22,English,,0,0,0,,And if the model returns something that's different, I tell them this is wrong.\N{\rChinese}如果模型返回的结果不同，我就告诉它这是错误的。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:21.44,English,,0,0,0,,And what the computer then does is refine this model until it becomes this.\N{\rChinese}于是电脑会把模型不断细化，直到它变成这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.88,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay?\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:28.64,English,,0,0,0,,So what all AI is is infinite iteration.\N{\rChinese}所以所有AI就是无穷迭代。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? All right.\N{\rChinese}好了？这有道理吗？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.30,English,,0,0,0,,All right. So\N{\rChinese}好的。那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.62,English,,0,0,0,,the problem with AI is I need\N{\rChinese}AI的问题是我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.54,English,,0,0,0,,to be able to solve three things.\N{\rChinese}能够解决三件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:45.56,English,,0,0,0,,And if I can solve three things, then I can create an AI.\N{\rChinese}如果我能解决三件事，那我就能造出一个AI。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:48.98,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? The first thing is that\N{\rChinese}好了？第一件事是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.96,English,,0,0,0,,I need\N{\rChinese}我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:57.48,English,,0,0,0,,clear metrics.\N{\rChinese}清晰的指标。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.96,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Or clear outputs.\N{\rChinese}好的？或者清晰的输出。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? I need outputs that\N{\rChinese}好的？那有道理吗？我需要的输出是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.36,English,,0,0,0,,I can define as a mathematical model.\N{\rChinese}我可以把它定义成一个数学模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.54,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, for example,\N{\rChinese}好的？比如说，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:12.58,English,,0,0,0,,if I'm an airline,\N{\rChinese}如果我是航空公司，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:17.14,English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use AI to maximize the amount of money I make on a flight.\N{\rChinese}我将使用人工智能来最大化每趟航班的收益。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.00,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Okay? That's my output.\N{\rChinese}对吧？好的？这就是我的输出。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.82,English,,0,0,0,,How much money can I make out of a flight?\N{\rChinese}一次航班能赚多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.04,English,,0,0,0,,I want to have the maximum amount of profit.\N{\rChinese}我想获得最大的利润。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.58,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's the first thing I need to solve.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是我需要先解决的第一件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:31.02,English,,0,0,0,,Second thing I need to solve then is to make sure that I have the right metrics.\N{\rChinese}第二件事我需要先解决的是确保我有正确的指标。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:38.48,English,,0,0,0,,But the way I figured this out is, let's try and figure out what are the standards.\N{\rChinese}我想出来的办法是，先试着弄清楚标准是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.94,English,,0,0,0,,But let's try and figure out what are the standards.\N{\rChinese}再试着弄清楚标准是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.74,English,,0,0,0,,But let's try and figure out what are the standards. But let's try and figure out what are the standards.\N{\rChinese}再试着弄清楚标准是什么。再试着弄清楚标准是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:48.14,English,,0,0,0,,But let's try and figure out what are the standards. But let's try and figure out what are the standards. But let's try and figure out what are the standards. But let's try and figure out what are the standards. But let's try and figure out what are the standards.\N{\rChinese}再试着弄清楚标准是什么。再试着弄清楚标准是什么。再试着弄清楚标准是什么。再试着弄清楚标准是什么。再试着弄清楚标准是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.86,English,,0,0,0,,But let's try and figure out what are the standards.\N{\rChinese}再试着弄清楚标准是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.76,English,,0,0,0,,But let's try and figure out what are the standards.\N{\rChinese}再试着弄清楚标准是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:59.50,English,,0,0,0,,But let's try and figure out what are the standards.\N{\rChinese}再试着弄清楚标准是什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.96,English,,0,0,0,,data sets of different animals.\N{\rChinese}不同动物的数据集。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, does that make sense? I need to label my data.\N{\rChinese}好的，听得懂吗？我得给我的数据打标签。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.58,English,,0,0,0,,But I can't tell,\N{\rChinese}但我说不出来，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:12.18,English,,0,0,0,,I can't make an AI that's like, this is the best ice cream in the world.\N{\rChinese}我没法让AI说这就是世界上最好的冰淇淇。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:16.74,English,,0,0,0,,And the reason why is, I can't find data\N{\rChinese}原因是，我找不到最佳冰淇淇的数据，你明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.72,English,,0,0,0,,on the best ice cream, you understand?\N{\rChinese}因为冰淇淇，最佳冰淇淇是主观的。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.12,English,,0,0,0,,Because ice cream, the best ice cream is subjective.\N{\rChinese}我无法把它变成数据集。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.76,English,,0,0,0,,So I cannot turn that into a data set.\N{\rChinese}于是我就把它变成数据集。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, does that make sense? Okay,\N{\rChinese}好的，听得懂吗？好的，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.76,English,,0,0,0,,the third thing I need to\N{\rChinese}第三件事我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.64,English,,0,0,0,,do is create a\N{\rChinese}做的是创建一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:33.96,English,,0,0,0,,working algorithm structure.\N{\rChinese}工作算法结构。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.68,English,,0,0,0,,You understand, okay?\N{\rChinese}你明白，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.64,English,,0,0,0,,Computers can only refine and optimize\N{\rChinese}计算机只能细化并优化算法结构，自己却不能创造它。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.36,English,,0,0,0,,the algorithm structure. It cannot create it by itself.\N{\rChinese}好的？如果我能完成这三件事，……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:52.12,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So if I'm able to do all three things,\N{\rChinese}Okay? So if I'm able to do all three things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.52,English,,0,0,0,,then I'm able to do all three things.\N{\rChinese}然后我就能完成这三件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.50,English,,0,0,0,,I can use AI to optimize\N{\rChinese}我可以用 AI 来优化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:01.74,English,,0,0,0,,what I wanted to optimize.\N{\rChinese}我想要优化的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right, any questions so far?\N{\rChinese}好的？到目前为止，任何问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:09.22,English,,0,0,0,,Before I move on? Okay?\N{\rChinese}在我继续之前？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:15.24,English,,0,0,0,,So what this means is that there are certain problems\N{\rChinese}所以这意味着有些问题是可以解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:19.04,English,,0,0,0,,that I can solve using AI, and\N{\rChinese}我可以用 AI 解决的事，和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:22.48,English,,0,0,0,,there are certain problems I cannot solve using AI, okay?\N{\rChinese}我可以用 AI 解决的事，还有我用 AI 解决不了的事，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.34,English,,0,0,0,,So what are easy problems?\N{\rChinese}那么什么是容易解决的问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:29.40,English,,0,0,0,,What are some of the problems that AI can solve, right? Well, for example, facial recognition technology,\N{\rChinese}AI 能解决哪些问题？比如人脸识别技术，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:34.02,English,,0,0,0,,okay? Also, translation software, right?\N{\rChinese}好的？还有翻译软件，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.58,English,,0,0,0,,I can create an optimal translation software.\N{\rChinese}我可以开发出最优的翻译软件。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.86,English,,0,0,0,,Also, recommendation engines, right?\N{\rChinese}还有推荐引擎，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.52,English,,0,0,0,,So if you watch a movie on Netflix,\N{\rChinese}所以如果你在 Netflix 看电影，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.62,English,,0,0,0,,it recommends another movie, right?\N{\rChinese}它会给你推荐另一部电影，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:51.62,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Now let me ask you this question.\N{\rChinese}好的？现在让我问你这个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.56,English,,0,0,0,,Can I ever solve,\N{\rChinese}我能解决自驾车吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:19:00.48,English,,0,0,0,,self -driving cars? Can I ever solve self -driving cars?\N{\rChinese}我能解决自驾车吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:05.00,English,,0,0,0,,Self -driving cars. Can cars drive by themselves?\N{\rChinese}自驾车。汽车能自己开吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.38,English,,0,0,0,,Yes or no? Yes.\N{\rChinese}是或否？是。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.66,English,,0,0,0,,Why yes, Sally?\N{\rChinese}为什么是，萨莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.52,English,,0,0,0,,Because they're on.\N{\rChinese}因为它们在路上。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:18.76,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're driving. Okay, the answer is no.\N{\rChinese}我的意思是它们在行驶。好的，答案是没有。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:23.76,English,,0,0,0,,Why is the answer no? Okay, the answer no is,\N{\rChinese}为什么答案是没有？好的，答案是没有是，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:29.30,English,,0,0,0,,whatever I do, okay, I cannot solve something called the edge case.\N{\rChinese}无论我做什么，好的，我无法解决所谓的边缘情况。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:37.32,English,,0,0,0,,The edge case is, if the car is on the road,\N{\rChinese}边缘情况是，如果汽车在路上，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:41.64,English,,0,0,0,,what could happen that would screw up my AI system?\N{\rChinese}会发生什么能把我的 AI 系统搞乱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.88,English,,0,0,0,,You guys know? Why can't self -driving cars be solved?\N{\rChinese}你们知道吗？为什么自动驾驶汽车还没搞定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.40,English,,0,0,0,,Why can't we have self -driving cars on the road?\N{\rChinese}为什么我们还没能让自动驾驶汽车上路？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.02,English,,0,0,0,,What's an edge case?\N{\rChinese}什么是边缘情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.50,English,,0,0,0,,Or this thing that I can never solve?\N{\rChinese}或者这件我永远解不出来的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:03.72,English,,0,0,0,,What is it? Excuse me?\N{\rChinese}它是什么？请问一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.14,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and what is not planned?\N{\rChinese}是的，什么没被计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.34,English,,0,0,0,,Hm? They can plan for traffic.\N{\rChinese}嗯？他们能预先安排交通。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.70,English,,0,0,0,,What can they not plan for?\N{\rChinese}他们还能预先安排什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.58,English,,0,0,0,,And this is why we'll never have someone driving cars.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们永远不会有人开车的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.46,English,,0,0,0,,They can plan for accidents. What can they not plan for?\N{\rChinese}他们能预先安排事故。还有什么能预先安排？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:27.66,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Easily plan for traffic rules.\N{\rChinese}嗯？很容易预先安排交通规则。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:32.56,English,,0,0,0,,What can they not plan for? Okay, guys.\N{\rChinese}还有什么能预先安排？好了，大家。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:37.08,English,,0,0,0,,The edge case with self -driving cars is if I,\N{\rChinese}边缘情况是自驾车，如果我，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:41.10,English,,0,0,0,,as a human being, intentionally want to crash into that car.\N{\rChinese}作为人类，故意想撞上那辆车。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:46.52,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? Does that make sense to you guys?\N{\rChinese}你们明白吗？这对你们来说有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.86,English,,0,0,0,,Every other situation I can plan for.\N{\rChinese}我能预先安排的其他情况都已列举。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.88,English,,0,0,0,,But in a situation where I'm the human being,\N{\rChinese}但在我作为人类的情形里，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.72,English,,0,0,0,,and I don't like self -driving cars because I'm a taxi driver,\N{\rChinese}我不喜欢自驾车，因为我是出租车司机。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:58.04,English,,0,0,0,,and it's stealing my job, right?\N{\rChinese}它正在抢走我的工作，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.84,English,,0,0,0,,It's stealing my livelihood, and I want to crash into that car.\N{\rChinese}它正在抢走我的生计，我想撞上那辆车。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.34,English,,0,0,0,,There's no way for that\N{\rChinese}没有办法了。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:06.08,English,,0,0,0,,AI to avoid the accident.\N{\rChinese}AI去避免事故。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.10,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay?\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.44,English,,0,0,0,,Listen. Listen.\N{\rChinese}听着。听着。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.86,English,,0,0,0,,AI is a scam, okay?\N{\rChinese}AI是个骗局，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.76,English,,0,0,0,,It does not exist. What exists?\N{\rChinese}它不存在。存在的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.34,English,,0,0,0,,What exists is supervised machine learning, okay?\N{\rChinese}存在的是监督式机器学习，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:26.44,English,,0,0,0,,What is supervised machine learning? What I just told you, okay?\N{\rChinese}什么是监督式机器学习？我刚才说的，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.80,English,,0,0,0,,That's it. That's the extent of our technology.\N{\rChinese}就是这样。就是我们的技术范围。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:32.28,English,,0,0,0,,It does not have self -awareness.\N{\rChinese}它没有自我意识。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:36.12,English,,0,0,0,,It can only do what the algorithm tells it to do.\N{\rChinese}它只能执行算法指令的动作。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.18,English,,0,0,0,,And there's no way you can design an algorithm that\N{\rChinese}而且你无法设计出一个能预先规划并预防人类动作的算法。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:42.74,English,,0,0,0,,plans for and prevents a human being\N{\rChinese}它计划并预防人类动作的算法也不存在。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.94,English,,0,0,0,,who intentionally wants to crash into you.\N{\rChinese}谁故意撞上你。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? All right?\N{\rChinese}好？这样说通吗？没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.84,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So AI, in other words,\N{\rChinese}好？所以AI，换句话说，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:53.46,English,,0,0,0,,is actually a limited tool, okay?\N{\rChinese}它实际上是一个有限工具，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:58.66,English,,0,0,0,,So you think about actual applications of AI, it's very limited.\N{\rChinese}所以你在考虑AI的实际应用时，它很有限。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:01.02,English,,0,0,0,,You also look at self -driving cars.\N{\rChinese}你还会看自驾车。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:04.82,English,,0,0,0,,Now, there are cars that have self -driving features,\N{\rChinese}现在，有些车配备了自动驾驶功能，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.90,English,,0,0,0,,but they are not 100% self -driving.\N{\rChinese}但它们并非百分百自动驾驶。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? In fact, they tell you,\N{\rChinese}好？这样说通吗？实际上，它们会告诉你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:14.78,English,,0,0,0,,don't rely on the autopilot, okay?\N{\rChinese}不靠自动驾驶，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:16.82,English,,0,0,0,,It's there to help you,\N{\rChinese}它是来帮你的，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:19.84,English,,0,0,0,,but don't sleep in the car.\N{\rChinese}但别在车里睡觉。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:24.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Right? Because\N{\rChinese}好？对吗？因为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:27.04,English,,0,0,0,,they don't have an AI system\N{\rChinese}它们没有 AI 系统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:31.64,English,,0,0,0,,in place to prevent people from crashing into them.\N{\rChinese}来防止人们撞上它们。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.76,0:22:33.84,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? All right.\N{\rChinese}好？这样说通吗？好。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:36.38,English,,0,0,0,,So now that we know what AI is,\N{\rChinese}现在我们知道 AI 是什么了，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:39.60,English,,0,0,0,,let's talk about how we can use AI\N{\rChinese}接下来聊聊我们如何使用 AI。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.12,English,,0,0,0,,to predict the future.\N{\rChinese}预测未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Okay?\N{\rChinese}好？好？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.46,English,,0,0,0,,All right. All right.\N{\rChinese}好。好。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:53.20,English,,0,0,0,,So basically, what you need to do is three things,\N{\rChinese}所以基本上，你需要做三件事，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:56.58,English,,0,0,0,,right? You need to be clear about the output,\N{\rChinese}对吧？你要把输出弄清楚，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:59.22,English,,0,0,0,,you need to have clean data,\N{\rChinese}你要有干净的数据。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:03.66,English,,0,0,0,,and you need to have a working algorithm.\N{\rChinese}并且你需要有一个可用的算法。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:05.84,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:10.46,English,,0,0,0,,And so that's what I've been doing this semester.\N{\rChinese}于是这就是我本学期所做的工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.12,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So for example,\N{\rChinese}好的？比如说，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.10,English,,0,0,0,,remember my predictions.\N{\rChinese}记住我的预测。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:18.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:23.54,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? if you go to a legal lobby, Saudi Arabia\N{\rChinese}好的？如果你去法律游说，沙特阿拉伯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.82,English,,0,0,0,,and the American Empire,\N{\rChinese}和美帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:30.08,English,,0,0,0,,basically the need to protect the petrodollar,\N{\rChinese}基本上是要保护石油美元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:35.86,English,,0,0,0,,will force America to go to war with Iran.\N{\rChinese}将迫使美国与伊朗开战。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:39.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? These are the push factors.\N{\rChinese}好的吗？这些是推动因素。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.88,English,,0,0,0,,The problem is that\N{\rChinese}问题在于…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:47.22,English,,0,0,0,,there are no force to counteract this, okay?\N{\rChinese}没有力量去抵消这件事，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.26,English,,0,0,0,,So for example, the military.\N{\rChinese}比如说，军队。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:54.10,English,,0,0,0,,The military will be for this because\N{\rChinese}军队会为此而行动。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:57.86,English,,0,0,0,,they have shock and awe, and they are very confident they can win this war.\N{\rChinese}他们震惊又敬畏，且十分自信能赢得这场战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:02.24,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Iran itself wants this war\N{\rChinese}好的吗？伊朗本身也想要这场战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:04.52,English,,0,0,0,,because it wants revenge\N{\rChinese}因为它想报仇。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:07.52,English,,0,0,0,,against America. Okay?\N{\rChinese}对美国的行动。好的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:11.16,English,,0,0,0,,And then the President of the United States, will be Donald Trump,\N{\rChinese}随后美国总统将是唐纳德·特朗普，
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:14.96,English,,0,0,0,,he wants this war in order to cement his position\N{\rChinese}他想发动这场战争以巩固自己的地位。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:19.24,English,,0,0,0,,as President. Okay? And so,\N{\rChinese}作为总统。好的吗？于是，
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:21.94,English,,0,0,0,,because of this, we can predict that\N{\rChinese}因为这样，我们可以预测
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:24.78,English,,0,0,0,,there'll be a war in Iran.\N{\rChinese}将会有一场伊朗战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.52,0:24:28.06,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay.\N{\rChinese}那有道理吗？好。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.55,0:24:31.68,English,,0,0,0,,Now, given this prediction,\N{\rChinese}现在，基于这个预测，
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.92,0:24:36.00,English,,0,0,0,,what we can then do is use mathematical modeling\N{\rChinese}接下来我们可以做的是使用数学建模
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:40.58,English,,0,0,0,,and statistics to turn this into an AI model.\N{\rChinese}并用统计数据把它变成一个AI模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.95,0:24:43.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好？这样有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:49.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Now we have the AI model.\N{\rChinese}好？现在我们已经有了AI模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.64,0:24:53.18,English,,0,0,0,,Now that we have the AI model,\N{\rChinese}现在我们已经有了AI模型，
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.54,0:24:57.74,English,,0,0,0,,what we need to do now is to refine it.\N{\rChinese}接下来我们需要做的是对它进行细化。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.02,0:25:02.62,English,,0,0,0,,And the way we refined it is by going back in history\N{\rChinese}细化的方法是回溯历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.62,0:25:06.10,English,,0,0,0,,and looking at every single war that started.\N{\rChinese}并且查看每一次战争的起始。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.84,0:25:09.22,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? And so,\N{\rChinese}这样有道理吗？于是，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.28,0:25:13.30,English,,0,0,0,,you take this model and you look at the different wars.\N{\rChinese}你拿起这个模型，去查看不同的战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.58,0:25:17.24,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So for example, the 415 BCE war.\N{\rChinese}好的？比如说公元前415年的战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.98,0:25:20.98,English,,0,0,0,,The invasion of Sicily by Athens.\N{\rChinese}雅典入侵西西里岛。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.02,0:25:24.10,English,,0,0,0,,You look at 1941,\N{\rChinese}你看1941年。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:26.04,English,,0,0,0,,Operation Barbarossa. Okay?\N{\rChinese}巴巴罗萨行动。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.20,0:25:29.56,English,,0,0,0,,You have basically hundreds of wars that you can look at.\N{\rChinese}你基本上有数百场战争可以去研究。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.98,0:25:33.62,English,,0,0,0,,And then you take this model and then you test it\N{\rChinese}然后你拿起这个模型，再去测试它。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.14,0:25:35.42,English,,0,0,0,,using each of these wars.\N{\rChinese}使用这些战争中的每一场。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.62,0:25:38.08,English,,0,0,0,,And what will happen is that\N{\rChinese}接下来会发生的事是……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.08,0:25:41.48,English,,0,0,0,,the model will begin to refine itself.\N{\rChinese}模型会开始自我精炼。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:44.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好的？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.36,0:25:46.00,English,,0,0,0,,So it becomes more and more refined.\N{\rChinese}于是它会越来越精细。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.42,0:25:53.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But then\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.86,0:25:56.62,English,,0,0,0,,that's one model for what causes war.\N{\rChinese}那是一个解释战争原因的模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.54,0:25:59.94,English,,0,0,0,,I've also said that\N{\rChinese}我也说过，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.94,0:26:02.96,English,,0,0,0,,Trump will become president.\N{\rChinese}特朗普将成为总统。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.12,0:26:06.00,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Well\N{\rChinese}对吗？好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.00,0:26:08.54,English,,0,0,0,,then, that's another model that you can use.\N{\rChinese}然后，这又是一个你可以使用的模型
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.92,0:26:11.76,English,,0,0,0,,And once you start putting all these models together,\N{\rChinese}一旦你开始把所有这些模型组合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:14.34,English,,0,0,0,,what eventually happens is,\N{\rChinese}最终发生的事是，
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.36,0:26:18.48,English,,0,0,0,,what happens over time is you develop cycle history.\N{\rChinese}随着时间推移，你会形成循环历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.64,0:26:23.40,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does this make sense, guys?\N{\rChinese}这样说清楚吗，大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.86,0:26:27.96,English,,0,0,0,,All right? So now the question then is,\N{\rChinese}好的？那么现在的问题是，
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.34,0:26:34.02,English,,0,0,0,,okay, how would this AI model work?\N{\rChinese}好的，这个AI模型怎么运作？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.30,0:26:38.86,English,,0,0,0,,Or what are the ideas behind this model?\N{\rChinese}或者这个模型背后的想法是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.10,0:26:40.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So\N{\rChinese}好的？那么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.80,0:26:44.34,English,,0,0,0,,we talk about game theory analysis a lot.\N{\rChinese}我们经常谈论博弈论分析。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.88,0:26:50.86,English,,0,0,0,,All right? And the idea of game theory analysis is\N{\rChinese}好的？博弈论分析的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.86,0:26:55.04,English,,0,0,0,,that, okay, guys, there's really no good and evil.\N{\rChinese}那，好吧，大家，真的没有好与坏。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.54,0:26:58.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? There are different players in a game.\N{\rChinese}好吧？游戏里有不同的玩家。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.02,0:27:01.26,English,,0,0,0,,And they're all self -interested.\N{\rChinese}他们都是自利的。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.40,0:27:03.08,English,,0,0,0,,They all want to win this game.\N{\rChinese}他们都想赢得这场游戏。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:05.82,English,,0,0,0,,So they're going to develop strategies that\N{\rChinese}于是他们会制定策略，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.82,0:27:09.14,English,,0,0,0,,optimize their ability to win this game.\N{\rChinese}以优化自己赢得这场游戏的能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.30,0:27:12.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So you can use game theory analysis.\N{\rChinese}好吧？那么你可以用博弈论来分析。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.44,0:27:16.06,English,,0,0,0,,But then you can also use, you know, you can also develop new ideas\N{\rChinese}但随后你也可以用，你知道，你也可以提出新的想法。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.06,0:27:17.86,English,,0,0,0,,that\N{\rChinese}那。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:22.36,English,,0,0,0,,would help you better understand how the world works.\N{\rChinese}这将帮助你更好地理解世界运作方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.26,0:27:27.60,English,,0,0,0,,So let's talk about some ideas\N{\rChinese}那么我们来聊聊本课程中出现的一些想法。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.60,0:27:30.82,English,,0,0,0,,that have come up in this course.\N{\rChinese}这些想法已经在本课程中浮现。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.40,0:27:32.74,English,,0,0,0,,All right? So\N{\rChinese}好的？那么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.74,0:27:38.66,English,,0,0,0,,one thing I want to talk about is this week's European elections.\N{\rChinese}我想谈谈本周的欧洲选举。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.40,0:27:40.76,English,,0,0,0,,Have you guys seen the news?\N{\rChinese}你们看过新闻了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.76,0:27:45.46,English,,0,0,0,,The elections to the European Parliament.\N{\rChinese}欧洲议会选举。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.76,0:27:47.38,English,,0,0,0,,Right? And\N{\rChinese}好吧？而且
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.38,0:27:50.60,English,,0,0,0,,the results are pretty shocking.\N{\rChinese}结果相当震撼。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.12,0:27:56.62,English,,0,0,0,,Because it signals a clear shift to the right.\N{\rChinese}因为它表明了向右的明显转变。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.32,0:27:59.80,English,,0,0,0,,So, for example,\N{\rChinese}于是，例如，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.40,0:28:07.32,English,,0,0,0,,Marylepain's party in France picked up a lot of votes.\N{\rChinese}玛丽勒潘在法国的党派获得了大量选票。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.08,0:28:11.14,English,,0,0,0,,The AFD, the Alternative for Germany, the Alternative for Germany, which\N{\rChinese}德国之路，德国之路，德国之路，哪一支是德国的替代党，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.14,0:28:13.74,English,,0,0,0,,is considered a right -wing organization,\N{\rChinese}它被认为是右派组织，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.14,0:28:18.86,English,,0,0,0,,almost neo -Nazi, has picked up a lot of votes as well.\N{\rChinese}几乎是新纳粟，已获得大量选票。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.42,0:28:22.30,English,,0,0,0,,The results were so dramatic\N{\rChinese}结果如此戏剧性
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.30,0:28:25.42,English,,0,0,0,,that Emmanuel Macron, the president of France,\N{\rChinese}埃马纽埃尔·马克龙，法国总统，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:27.20,English,,0,0,0,,has called for an early election.\N{\rChinese}他已呼吁提前选举。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.58,0:28:29.74,English,,0,0,0,,And it's possible in three months' time,\N{\rChinese}好的？三个月后，玛丽莱潘的党派将执政法国。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.12,0:28:33.92,English,,0,0,0,,Marylepain's party will run and govern France.\N{\rChinese}好的？于是……
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.08,0:28:36.08,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.08,0:28:40.04,English,,0,0,0,,how do we explain this shift to the right?\N{\rChinese}我们怎么解释这一下右移？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.92,0:28:44.70,English,,0,0,0,,And I want to explain three reasons.\N{\rChinese}我想解释三个原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.78,0:28:50.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? The first reason is anti -immigration.\N{\rChinese}第一个原因是反移民。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.24,0:28:58.58,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So for the past 10,\N{\rChinese}好的？所以过去十年，二十年，欧洲从利比亚、叙利亚、伊拉克涌入了大量移民。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.66,0:29:02.58,English,,0,0,0,,20 years, there have been a lot of immigrants to Europe from Libya,\N{\rChinese}好的？所以过去十年，二十年，欧洲从利比亚、叙利亚、伊拉克涌入了大量移民。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.86,0:29:04.42,English,,0,0,0,,from Syria, from Iraq,\N{\rChinese}好的？所以过去十年，二十年，欧洲从利比亚、叙利亚、伊拉克涌入了大量移民。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.86,0:29:07.78,English,,0,0,0,,Afghanistan, Sudan, Somalia.\N{\rChinese}阿富汗、苏丹、索马里。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.96,0:29:10.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? These are mainly non -immigrants.\N{\rChinese}好的吗？这些主要是非移民。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.02,0:29:13.48,English,,0,0,0,,They are Muslim people who\N{\rChinese}他们是穆斯林人。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.48,0:29:18.64,English,,0,0,0,,threaten the Christian social fabric of Europe.\N{\rChinese}威胁欧洲基督教社会结构。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.04,0:29:23.72,English,,0,0,0,,And now Europeans are rebelling or revolting against that.\N{\rChinese}现在欧洲人对此起了反抗或起了革命。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.71,0:29:28.36,English,,0,0,0,,Second thing that they don't like about Europe\N{\rChinese}第二件他们不喜欢的关于欧洲的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.36,0:29:30.92,English,,0,0,0,,so far is the idea of federalism.\N{\rChinese}到目前为止是联邦主义的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.52,0:29:34.98,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Or they can say bureaucratism.\N{\rChinese}好的吗？或者他们可以说官僚主义。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.75,0:29:39.80,English,,0,0,0,,But this idea that a foreign power,\N{\rChinese}但这种概念是外部势力，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.02,0:29:42.94,English,,0,0,0,,Brussels, mandates rules\N{\rChinese}布鲁塞尔，授权规则
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.94,0:29:44.98,English,,0,0,0,,that they must follow.\N{\rChinese}那他们必须遵循的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.68,0:29:47.70,English,,0,0,0,,So they think it's very anti -democratic.\N{\rChinese}于是他们认为这很反民主。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.96,0:29:50.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the third thing\N{\rChinese}好的吗？还有第三点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.94,0:29:52.36,English,,0,0,0,,that\N{\rChinese}是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.36,0:29:56.20,English,,0,0,0,,they're rebelling against is the idea of pan -Europeanism.\N{\rChinese}他们所反叛的，是泛欧洲主义的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.10,0:30:01.36,English,,0,0,0,,What the people of Europe are saying is,\N{\rChinese}欧洲人民所说的是，
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.54,0:30:04.32,English,,0,0,0,,there's no European identity, guys.\N{\rChinese}没有欧洲身份，大家。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.52,0:30:07.46,English,,0,0,0,,There's a German identity, there's a French identity, Italian,\N{\rChinese}有德国身份，有法国身份，意大利身份，
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.84,0:30:11.08,English,,0,0,0,,Spanish, Portuguese, but there's no European identity.\N{\rChinese}西班牙语、葡萄牙语，但没有欧洲身份。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.40,0:30:15.52,English,,0,0,0,,They're rebelling against the entire project of the EU.\N{\rChinese}他们正反叛欧盟的整个项目。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:18.62,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, I would bet that\N{\rChinese}实际上，我打赌是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.62,0:30:21.12,English,,0,0,0,,in about five years' time, the entire EU\N{\rChinese}大约五年后，整个欧盟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.30,0:30:23.58,English,,0,0,0,,would be dead. Okay?\N{\rChinese}会死的。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.80,0:30:28.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Why are they opposed to\N{\rChinese}为什么他们反对？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.18,0:30:33.54,English,,0,0,0,,pan -Europeanism?\N{\rChinese}泛欧主义？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.00,0:30:37.70,English,,0,0,0,,Because, ultimately, they believe\N{\rChinese}因为，最终，他们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.00,0:30:42.44,English,,0,0,0,,that it's about destroying local identity.\N{\rChinese}那是关于消灭地方身份的。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.66,0:30:44.74,English,,0,0,0,,It's about destroying local community.\N{\rChinese}那是关于消灭地方社区的。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.06,0:30:49.18,English,,0,0,0,,It's about destroying my relationship with my neighbors\N{\rChinese}关于破坏我与邻居的关系以及我的朋友和亲戚。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.18,0:30:52.20,English,,0,0,0,,and my friends and my relatives.\N{\rChinese}关于破坏我与邻居的关系以及我的朋友和亲戚。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.34,0:30:54.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And my family. Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好的？还有我的家人。这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:31:00.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? It's imposing a foreign identity on me. And\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是把外来身份强加在我身上。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:06.04,English,,0,0,0,,proponents of\N{\rChinese}主张者
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.04,0:31:09.40,English,,0,0,0,,the European Union would argue\N{\rChinese}欧盟会说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.40,0:31:12.12,English,,0,0,0,,that, no, this is just a secular,\N{\rChinese}那，没错，这只是一个世俗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.70,0:31:17.94,English,,0,0,0,,liberal idea.\N{\rChinese}自由主义理念。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.56,0:31:21.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? The entire idea of the EU is\N{\rChinese}好吧？欧盟的整体理念是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.70,0:31:25.56,English,,0,0,0,,that for hundreds of years, thousands of years,\N{\rChinese}那几百年、几千年，欧洲一直处于战争之中。为什么欧洲一直处于战争之中？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.02,0:31:28.82,English,,0,0,0,,Europe has been at war. Why has Europe been at war?\N{\rChinese}Europe has been at war. Why has Europe been at war?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.20,0:31:30.80,English,,0,0,0,,Tribalism, right? Religion.\N{\rChinese}部落主义，对吧？宗教。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.34,0:31:35.93,English,,0,0,0,,So the entire project of the EU is to get rid of\N{\rChinese}于是欧盟的整个项目就是摆脱……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.18,0:31:40.50,English,,0,0,0,,this the factors that lead to war.\N{\rChinese}这就是导致战争的因素。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.72,0:31:42.26,English,,0,0,0,,Local identity, nationalism,\N{\rChinese}地方身份，民族主义，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.64,0:31:43.98,English,,0,0,0,,religion. Right?\N{\rChinese}宗教。对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.56,0:31:48.24,English,,0,0,0,,And what the European voters are saying to the EU is,\N{\rChinese}欧洲选民对欧盟说的是，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.40,0:31:50.26,English,,0,0,0,,um, sorry,\N{\rChinese}嗯，抱歉，我们不想要世俗自由主义
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.54,0:31:53.52,English,,0,0,0,,we don't want secular liberalism because\N{\rChinese}we don't want secular liberalism because
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.52,0:31:58.28,English,,0,0,0,,we want to be human. Okay?\N{\rChinese}我们想成为人类。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.72,0:32:03.96,English,,0,0,0,,What we strive for is not a abstract,\N{\rChinese}我们所追求的不是抽象，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.34,0:32:05.66,English,,0,0,0,,liberal idea.\N{\rChinese}自由理念。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:08.24,English,,0,0,0,,We strive for structure,\N{\rChinese}我们追求结构，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.64,0:32:15.30,English,,0,0,0,,meaning, and purpose in our lives.\N{\rChinese}意义与目的。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.30,0:32:21.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? What we really strive for is the capacity to love,\N{\rChinese}好的？我们真正追求的是爱、创作与学习的能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.86,0:32:24.24,English,,0,0,0,,create, and learn.\N{\rChinese}好的？并且成长。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.46,0:32:25.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And grow.\N{\rChinese}Okay? And grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.62,0:32:32.16,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? That's what we are fundamentally as human beings.\N{\rChinese}那有道理吗？这就是我们人类的根本。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.84,0:32:34.72,English,,0,0,0,,And when you ask me\N{\rChinese}当你问我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.28,0:32:39.34,English,,0,0,0,,to obey an abstract foreign entity\N{\rChinese}去服从一个抽象的外部实体
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:42.92,English,,0,0,0,,that is very far from me,\N{\rChinese}那离我很远，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.06,0:32:48.44,English,,0,0,0,,then you are limiting or destroying the structure,\N{\rChinese}然后你就限制或破坏结构，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.58,0:32:51.52,English,,0,0,0,,meaning, and purpose in my life.\N{\rChinese}意义与目的在我的生活中。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.52,0:32:55.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And so, that's what's going on,\N{\rChinese}好的？于是，事情就是这样，正在发生的事，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.08,0:32:58.46,English,,0,0,0,,not just in Europe, but throughout the world.\N{\rChinese}不只是欧洲，而是全世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.60,0:33:00.74,English,,0,0,0,,You think about Brexit, right?\N{\rChinese}你想想英国脱欧，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.80,0:33:04.48,English,,0,0,0,,You think about the election of Donald Trump, right?\N{\rChinese}你想想唐纳德·特朗普的当选，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.48,0:33:07.44,English,,0,0,0,,All these things have to do with this fundamental\N{\rChinese}所有这些事都与这个基本的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.04,0:33:13.20,English,,0,0,0,,human urge to have structure, meaning,\N{\rChinese}人类有结构、意义的本能有关。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.32,0:33:16.58,English,,0,0,0,,and purpose in our lives.\N{\rChinese}以及我们生活中的目的。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.66,0:33:21.78,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? To have agency. Okay?\N{\rChinese}好吧？拥有主导性。好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.82,0:33:23.76,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense, guys? All right.\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗，大家？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.78,0:33:26.82,English,,0,0,0,,Any questions so far? Yeah?\N{\rChinese}还有问题吗？对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.90,0:33:32.50,English,,0,0,0,,Eric? Okay.\N{\rChinese}埃里克？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.50,0:33:35.58,English,,0,0,0,,So, Eric asked, okay,\N{\rChinese}于是，埃里克问，好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.64,0:33:38.62,English,,0,0,0,,what is the source of all this?\N{\rChinese}什么是这一切的源头？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.44,0:33:43.72,English,,0,0,0,,And what Dante and Homer\N{\rChinese}而且但丁与荷马会说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.38,0:33:45.78,English,,0,0,0,,would say is\N{\rChinese}会说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.46,0:33:51.34,English,,0,0,0,,the human heart, okay? The human heart.\N{\rChinese}人心，好的？人心。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.78,0:33:54.26,English,,0,0,0,,This is just who we are.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.66,0:33:59.42,English,,0,0,0,,And if we cannot fulfill our human heart,\N{\rChinese}如果我们无法实现人心，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.54,0:34:00.76,English,,0,0,0,,we will rebel.\N{\rChinese}我们会起义。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.76,0:34:02.04,English,,0,0,0,,We will destroy.\N{\rChinese}我们会毁灭。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.52,0:34:03.88,English,,0,0,0,,We will want to kill.\N{\rChinese}我们会想要杀人。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:07.92,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And so, in other words,\N{\rChinese}好的？那么，换句话说，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.96,0:34:12.60,English,,0,0,0,,one idea in this AI model is\N{\rChinese}这个 AI 模型的一个想法是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.60,0:34:15.60,English,,0,0,0,,that there is a fundamental\N{\rChinese}有一个根本的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.60,0:34:19.96,English,,0,0,0,,underlying structure to human society.\N{\rChinese}基础结构属于人类社会。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.32,0:34:23.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? If society conforms\N{\rChinese}好？如果社会符合人心结构，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.36,0:34:26.94,English,,0,0,0,,to the structure of the human heart,\N{\rChinese}则……
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.12,0:34:29.48,English,,0,0,0,,this society will prosper.\N{\rChinese}这个社会将繁荣。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.48,0:34:31.38,English,,0,0,0,,For example, Athens,\N{\rChinese}例如，雅典，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.74,0:34:33.54,English,,0,0,0,,right? The ancient Greeks.\N{\rChinese}对吧？古希腊人。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.80,0:34:35.44,English,,0,0,0,,That society prospered.\N{\rChinese}那社会繁荣了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.54,0:34:38.20,English,,0,0,0,,The word we used was eudaimonia, right?\N{\rChinese}我们用的词是eudaimonia，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.16,0:34:41.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But if society\N{\rChinese}好？但如果社会
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.74,0:34:45.98,English,,0,0,0,,represses the human heart, then\N{\rChinese}压抑人心，随后
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:49.46,English,,0,0,0,,ultimately the society will have to collapse at some point.\N{\rChinese}最终社会必将在某时崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.52,0:34:54.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So,\N{\rChinese}好？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.40,0:34:59.06,English,,0,0,0,,that's another principle that we can use when developing this AI model.\N{\rChinese}那是我们在开发这个 AI 模型时可以使用的另一个原则。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.64,0:35:03.12,English,,0,0,0,,The last idea that\N{\rChinese}最后一个想法是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.12,0:35:08.28,English,,0,0,0,,we can use in developing this AI model is the idea of synchronicity.\N{\rChinese}我们在开发这个 AI 模型时可以使用的就是同步性。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.42,0:35:14.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Synchronicity. And\N{\rChinese}好？同步性。还有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.30,0:35:18.06,English,,0,0,0,,the idea of synchronicity is, as a society,\N{\rChinese}同步性的概念是，作为一个社会，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.44,0:35:20.84,English,,0,0,0,,how willing are people\N{\rChinese}人们愿意程度如何
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.88,0:35:26.70,English,,0,0,0,,how, how willing are people in following the rules?\N{\rChinese}人们遵守规则的愿意程度如何
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:31.48,English,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense. So, when you use the subway, do people actually follow traffic rules?\N{\rChinese}它有意义吗？那么，当你乘坐地铁时，人们真的会遵守交通规则吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.66,0:35:35.50,English,,0,0,0,,When you use the subway, do people actually give up their seats for the elderly,\N{\rChinese}当你乘坐地铁时，人们真的会把座位让给老人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.72,0:35:37.50,English,,0,0,0,,for children, for pregnant women?\N{\rChinese}为孩子、为孕妇？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.08,0:35:41.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? When you go to the park, do people actually pick up garbage\N{\rChinese}当你去公园时，人们真的会捡起垃圾吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.82,0:35:44.36,English,,0,0,0,,and throw it in the garbage bin?\N{\rChinese}并把它扔进垃圾桶？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.48,0:35:48.08,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Synchronicity tells us that there's\N{\rChinese}好的？同步性告诉我们……
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.44,0:35:53.08,English,,0,0,0,,cohesion and trust in society, that society is resilient,\N{\rChinese}团结与信任，社会的韧性，社会的可持续发展，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.90,0:35:57.80,English,,0,0,0,,okay? And that\N{\rChinese}好？以及那点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.80,0:36:01.62,English,,0,0,0,,society is resilient because society can grow, okay, or learn from its mistakes.\N{\rChinese}社会韧性在于其能够成长，或者从错误中学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.52,0:36:06.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, societies that are, that\N{\rChinese}好？所以，那些社会是，那些……
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:11.98,English,,0,0,0,,have high synchronicity will do better in the long term than societies with low synchronicity.\N{\rChinese}拥有高同步性的社会在长期表现上会优于低同步性的社会。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.26,0:36:15.82,English,,0,0,0,,And so, societies with high synchronicity would include Japan\N{\rChinese}而且，高同步性的社会包括日本
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.82,0:36:17.32,English,,0,0,0,,and Germany, right?\N{\rChinese}以及德国，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.90,0:36:20.24,English,,0,0,0,,And societies with low synchronicity would include\N{\rChinese}而低同步性的社会则包括
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.18,0:36:23.18,English,,0,0,0,,India and Brazil and China,\N{\rChinese}印度、巴西、中华，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.88,0:36:25.96,English,,0,0,0,,okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好？这样说对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.66,0:36:29.86,English,,0,0,0,,All right? So, when you go to the park, and\N{\rChinese}好的？所以，当你去公园时，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.86,0:36:38.80,English,,0,0,0,,you're totally\N{\rChinese}你完全是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.80,0:36:41.84,English,,0,0,0,,totally totally totally totally totally totally totally totally\N{\rChinese}完全完全完全完全完全完全完全完全
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.66,0:36:46.98,English,,0,0,0,,totally totally totally\N{\rChinese}完全完全完全
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.62,0:37:01.60,English,,0,0,0,,totally If you insert a human body into a human body,\N{\rChinese}完全如果你把一个人身体插进另一个人身体，那它为什么还是人身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.02,0:37:03.74,English,,0,0,0,,then why would it be a human body?\N{\rChinese}请问？那它为什么还是人身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.90,0:37:06.04,English,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? Why would it be a human body?\N{\rChinese}请问？那它为什么还是人身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.46,0:37:08.62,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's a great question. So\N{\rChinese}好的，这是个很好的问题。于是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.62,0:37:11.84,English,,0,0,0,,one thing that\N{\rChinese}有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.84,0:37:13.64,English,,0,0,0,,was not supposed to happen\N{\rChinese}本来应该发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.64,0:37:18.44,English,,0,0,0,,is the idea of mass society.\N{\rChinese}是大规模社会的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.52,0:37:22.54,English,,0,0,0,,Mass society. You can say that\N{\rChinese}大规模社会。你可以说它是……
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.54,0:37:25.18,English,,0,0,0,,mass society is a complete\N{\rChinese}大规模社会是完整的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.18,0:37:31.24,English,,0,0,0,,deviation from\N{\rChinese}偏离人类历史。我们本来没有大规模社会。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.24,0:37:35.60,English,,0,0,0,,human history. We're not supposed to have mass society.\N{\rChinese}而大规模社会完全是偶然的，历史的偶然。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.96,0:37:40.40,English,,0,0,0,,And mass society is completely an accident, a historical accident.\N{\rChinese}And mass society is completely anaccident, a historical accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.18,0:37:44.10,English,,0,0,0,,But when you have mass society, what happens is\N{\rChinese}但当你拥有大规模社会时，发生的事是……
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.10,0:37:46.30,English,,0,0,0,,that you need an elite.\N{\rChinese}你需要一个精英。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.98,0:37:51.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? You need an elite.\N{\rChinese}好的？你需要一个精英。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.86,0:37:56.44,English,,0,0,0,,But guess what, guys? The elite,\N{\rChinese}但你们猜怎么回事？精英，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.54,0:38:00.28,English,,0,0,0,,the people in charge, they're not better than you and me. Okay? You understand?\N{\rChinese}掌权的人们不比你我好。好吗？你懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.66,0:38:06.72,English,,0,0,0,,We in this classroom could swap\N{\rChinese}我们在这教室里可以互换
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.72,0:38:09.02,English,,0,0,0,,for the leadership of the world, right?\N{\rChinese}为世界的领导者，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.28,0:38:11.22,English,,0,0,0,,And guys, nothing would change.\N{\rChinese}而且，伙计们，什么也不会改变。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.94,0:38:15.24,English,,0,0,0,,You understand? Right?\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.46,0:38:18.42,English,,0,0,0,,So you have mass society, and therefore you have to have an artifact of mass society.\N{\rChinese}于是你拥有大众社会，因此你必须拥有大众社会的象征。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.42,0:38:22.40,English,,0,0,0,,And you have to have an elite. You have to have an elite. You have to have an elite. Because you need people in control.\N{\rChinese}你还得有精英。你得有精英。你得有精英。因为你需要掌权的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.96,0:38:24.44,English,,0,0,0,,And because they're in control,\N{\rChinese}因为他们掌权，
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.04,0:38:30.40,English,,0,0,0,,they need to now maintain the illusion of their power.\N{\rChinese}他们现在需要保持自己权力的幻象。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.64,0:38:34.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? They need to create fictions.\N{\rChinese}好吧？他们需要创造幻象。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.28,0:38:37.72,English,,0,0,0,,For example, maybe, well,\N{\rChinese}举例来说，可能是……
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.90,0:38:41.58,English,,0,0,0,,I went to Yale or Harvard, and therefore I should be at the top.\N{\rChinese}我去过耶鲁或哈佛，所以我应该在顶端。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.58,0:38:43.68,English,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I have a higher IQ than you do.\N{\rChinese}或者我智商比你高。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.78,0:38:48.64,English,,0,0,0,,Or maybe, you know, my dad or my great -great -great -great -grandfather was king.\N{\rChinese}或者，你知道，我的爸爸或我的曾曾曾曾祖父是国王。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.92,0:38:50.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? They had to create these fictions.\N{\rChinese}好吧？他们需要创造这些幻象。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.98,0:38:53.36,English,,0,0,0,,Now, what happens over time is that\N{\rChinese}现在，随着时间的推移，发生的事是……
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.36,0:38:56.38,English,,0,0,0,,these fictions fall apart because\N{\rChinese}这些幻象最终会崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.38,0:38:58.44,English,,0,0,0,,they're not that competent.\N{\rChinese}他们并不那么能干。
