Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.32,0:39:10.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? You look at the global management of war.\N{\rChinese}好吧？你看看全球战争管理。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.08,0:39:12.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? They're pretty incompetent.\N{\rChinese}好吧？他们相当不熟练。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.06,0:39:15.98,English,,0,0,0,,And so people sort of wake up and like, wait a minute.\N{\rChinese}于是人们会醒悟，稍等片刻。
