Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.54,0:43:07.58,English,,0,0,0,,let me explain how we would actually implement.\N{\rChinese}让我来说明我们实际如何实现
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.64,0:43:11.46,English,,0,0,0,,So first of all,\N{\rChinese}首先，
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.50,0:43:16.26,English,,0,0,0,,you need at least 50 to 100 years to actually create this AI.\N{\rChinese}你至少需要50到100年才能真正创建这个AI。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.54,0:43:19.04,English,,0,0,0,,And the reason why is that\N{\rChinese}原因是……
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.04,0:43:23.58,English,,0,0,0,,for this AI to be valid, you constantly need to be testing it.\N{\rChinese}为让这AI有效，你需要不断测试它。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.22,0:43:29.04,English,,0,0,0,,So what I've been doing in this class is basically doing a self -AI,\N{\rChinese}所以我在这节课里基本上做了一个自我AI，
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.04,0:43:33.00,English,,0,0,0,,where I have an analytical model and I have a prediction.\N{\rChinese}我有一个分析模型和一个预测。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.54,0:43:34.66,English,,0,0,0,,But guess what guys,\N{\rChinese}但你们猜怎么回事，
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.90,0:43:36.10,English,,0,0,0,,we won't know if my predictions\N{\rChinese}我们要等到现在起五十年后才能知道我的预测是否完全正确。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.10,0:43:41.86,English,,0,0,0,,are fully correct until 50 years from now.\N{\rChinese}are fully correct until 50 years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.00,0:43:44.10,English,,0,0,0,,Is that correct? Therefore,\N{\rChinese}那是对的吗？因此，
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.48,0:43:48.58,English,,0,0,0,,I can't validate my analysis until 50 years from now.\N{\rChinese}我要等到现在起五十年后才能验证我的分析。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.42,0:43:53.04,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? And you need to be constantly doing this\N{\rChinese}那有道理吗？你还得不断做这件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.04,0:43:56.76,English,,0,0,0,,where you have to be constantly making these predictions\N{\rChinese}你需要不断做这些预测
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.76,0:43:58.08,English,,0,0,0,,and seeing if they're correct or not.\N{\rChinese}并观察它们是否正确。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.20,0:43:59.80,English,,0,0,0,,If they're not correct, what you have to do is go and\N{\rChinese}若不正确，你就得去
