Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.30,0:44:07.10,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Then\N{\rChinese}那有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.10,0:44:11.06,English,,0,0,0,,what you have to do is you basically have to,\N{\rChinese}你需要做的事就是，你基本上要，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.12,0:44:15.46,English,,0,0,0,,and this is actually what's the most time consuming, you have to rewrite history.\N{\rChinese}这实际上是最耗时的，你要重新写历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.04,0:44:19.08,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? Because\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？
