Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.46,0:44:28.38,English,,0,0,0,,So what you have to do is you have to take this AI model and\N{\rChinese}所以你要做的事就是，你要拿这个AI模型来，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.88,0:44:31.40,English,,0,0,0,,look back at history and say,\N{\rChinese}回顾历史并说，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.52,0:44:35.84,English,,0,0,0,,according to this AI model, what actually happened in the Peloponnesian War?\N{\rChinese}根据这个AI模型，伯罗奔尼撒战争到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.02,0:44:42.44,English,,0,0,0,,What actually happened in World War I? What actually happened during the Tang Dynasty? So\N{\rChinese}第一次世界大战到底发生了什么？唐朝期间又发生了什么？于是
