Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.42,0:45:08.66,English,,0,0,0,,and seeing how history can be revamped or changed\N{\rChinese}观察历史如何被重塑或改写
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.66,0:45:11.24,English,,0,0,0,,so that it's more accurate.\N{\rChinese}使其更准确。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.44,0:45:14.28,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? That's a project,\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？这就是一个项目，
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.52,0:45:17.32,English,,0,0,0,,but then there's the technology.\N{\rChinese}然后才有技术。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.64,0:45:22.06,English,,0,0,0,,Because you actually need mathematicians and computer programmers and historians\N{\rChinese}因为你实际上需要数学家、电脑程序员和历史学家一起合作来构建这套 AI。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.74,0:45:25.62,English,,0,0,0,,to collaborate together to build this AI.\N{\rChinese}于是我可以告诉你我会如何分析这个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.30,0:45:33.20,English,,0,0,0,,So I can tell you how I would analyze the issue,\N{\rChinese}So I can tell you how Iwould analyze the issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.84,0:45:38.18,English,,0,0,0,,but then a mathematician has to turn this into a mathematical equation or a model.\N{\rChinese}但随后数学家必须把它转化为数学方程或模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.88,0:45:44.58,English,,0,0,0,,Because computers only recognize data and numbers.\N{\rChinese}因为计算机只识别数据和数字。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.82,0:45:47.38,English,,0,0,0,,They don't recognize ideas. I can't talk to a computer.\N{\rChinese}它们不识别概念。我无法与计算机对话。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.52,0:45:50.38,English,,0,0,0,,I have to give a computer a number\N{\rChinese}我得给电脑一个数字
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.38,0:45:54.86,English,,0,0,0,,or an equation or a model for it to calculate on.\N{\rChinese}或者一个方程式或模型让它去算
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.08,0:45:57.32,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}这样说对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.34,0:46:02.44,English,,0,0,0,,So it's not an easy project.\N{\rChinese}所以这不是一个简单的项目。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.46,0:46:05.98,English,,0,0,0,,But the argument is that\N{\rChinese}但论点是，
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.98,0:46:09.12,English,,0,0,0,,if this project actually works,\N{\rChinese}如果这个项目真的能成功，
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.22,0:46:11.66,English,,0,0,0,,it would change the fate of humanity forever.\N{\rChinese}它将永远改变人类的命运。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.08,0:46:15.24,English,,0,0,0,,Because if there's one thing that you notice in this class,\N{\rChinese}因为如果你在这门课里注意到一件事，
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.60,0:46:19.58,English,,0,0,0,,it's that we tend to repeat the same mistakes.\N{\rChinese}就是我们往往重复同样的错误。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.00,0:46:22.88,English,,0,0,0,,The question is, why do we do that?\N{\rChinese}问题是，为什么我们会这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.16,0:46:26.22,English,,0,0,0,,It's because, the history that\N{\rChinese}因为我们掌握的历史完全是胡说八道。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:29.16,English,,0,0,0,,we have is complete bullshit.\N{\rChinese}we have is complete bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.84,0:46:31.82,English,,0,0,0,,It just is. It's not true.\N{\rChinese}它就是这样。不是那样。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.90,0:46:34.28,English,,0,0,0,,It can't be true. Okay?\N{\rChinese}它就不是那样。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.48,0:46:39.02,English,,0,0,0,,There's things that we believe, which\N{\rChinese}有些我们相信的事物，若你想一想，肯定不对。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.02,0:46:42.10,English,,0,0,0,,if you just think about it, can't be true.\N{\rChinese}if you just think about it, can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.36,0:46:48.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And we did that like last semester when we talked about the rise of Christianity, right? You're telling me that\N{\rChinese}好的？我们像上学期那样讨论基督教的崛起时也是这么说的，对吧？你告诉我这位文盲叫耶稣的人能独自传播基督教。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.34,0:46:54.06,English,,0,0,0,,this illiterate guy named Jesus was able to spread Christianity all by himself,\N{\rChinese}this illiterate guy named Jesus was able to spread Christianity all by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.16,0:46:55.94,English,,0,0,0,,after he died? I don't believe that.\N{\rChinese}他死后呢？我不这么认为。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.30,0:46:59.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? I think a much easier explanation is that\N{\rChinese}我想更简单的解释是……
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.06,0:47:03.68,English,,0,0,0,,it became co -opted by the Roman Empire in order to control the Empire.\N{\rChinese}它被罗马帝国合并，以控制帝国。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.10,0:47:07.18,English,,0,0,0,,Right? But if you would talk to a historian,\N{\rChinese}对吧？但如果你去跟一位历史学家聊，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.38,0:47:10.02,English,,0,0,0,,they would say, you're just wrong.\N{\rChinese}他们会说，你刚才说错了。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.24,0:47:13.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, not only are you trying to predict the future,\N{\rChinese}好的？所以，你不仅在预测未来，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.58,0:47:17.98,English,,0,0,0,,but you're trying to also correct the past, which is, I think, an even more difficult job.\N{\rChinese}但你也在尝试纠正过去，我想这更是个更难的工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.12,0:47:20.78,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}对吧？还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.08,0:47:24.44,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Eric?.\N{\rChinese}嗯，埃里克？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.84,0:47:32.12,English,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? Oh, so, Eric asked a great question.\N{\rChinese}请问一下？哦，原来埃里克提了个好问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.70,0:47:35.86,English,,0,0,0,,Will this cycle history model encounter edge cases?\N{\rChinese}这个循环历史模型会遇到边缘案例吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.94,0:47:37.84,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is, that's the best question, okay?\N{\rChinese}答案是：这才是最好的问题，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.92,0:47:39.52,English,,0,0,0,,That's a great question. And the answer is,\N{\rChinese}这是个好问题。答案是，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.98,0:47:41.36,English,,0,0,0,,yes. What are edge cases?\N{\rChinese}是的。边缘案例是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.56,0:47:45.88,English,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know? What are edge cases in this model?\N{\rChinese}你们知道吗？这个模型中的边缘案例是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.84,0:47:51.20,English,,0,0,0,,. Who,\N{\rChinese}谁，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.32,0:47:53.88,English,,0,0,0,,what would be edge cases here in history?\N{\rChinese}这里的边缘案例是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.36,0:47:58.44,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's called great man theory, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的，叫做伟人理论，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.96,0:48:03.48,English,,0,0,0,,Great man theory. And this is a problem.\N{\rChinese}伟人理论。这是一个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.02,0:48:06.92,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning, like, okay, we believe,\N{\rChinese}意思是，好吧，我们认为，
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.30,0:48:10.30,English,,0,0,0,,we argue that\N{\rChinese}我们主张
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.30,0:48:14.96,English,,0,0,0,,these underlying historical forces control humanity,\N{\rChinese}这些潜在的历史力量主宰人类
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.26,0:48:19.38,English,,0,0,0,,right? But now and then, you have this great man coming out of nowhere,\N{\rChinese}对吧？但时不时，你会出现一个从无名处出现的伟人，他永远改变人类历史的进程，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.58,0:48:22.68,English,,0,0,0,,and he changes the course of human history forever, okay?\N{\rChinese}例子是，在我们有荷马之前，…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.98,0:48:27.28,English,,0,0,0,,The example is, before we had Homer,\N{\rChinese}The example is,before we had Homer,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.52,0:48:29.84,English,,0,0,0,,right? Then we had Dante.\N{\rChinese}对吧？然后我们有但丁。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.98,0:48:33.04,English,,0,0,0,,Then we had Plato,\N{\rChinese}然后我们有柏拉图。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.42,0:48:36.28,English,,0,0,0,,Jesus, Julius Caesar,\N{\rChinese}耶稣、朱利斯·凯撒。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.60,0:48:40.02,English,,0,0,0,,Octavius, Poutin today, okay?\N{\rChinese}八月维乌斯，普丁今天，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.14,0:48:43.46,English,,0,0,0,,We can't account for these people, because by definition,\N{\rChinese}我们无法解释这些人，因为按定义，
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.82,0:48:45.82,English,,0,0,0,,they're beyond, you know, beyond history.\N{\rChinese}他们已经超越，您知道，超越历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.36,0:48:50.32,English,,0,0,0,,They can step outside of history and control history.\N{\rChinese}他们可以跳出历史并掌控历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.74,0:48:55.34,English,,0,0,0,,That's what great men are. So how does your model account for that?\N{\rChinese}这就是伟人之所在。那你的模型如何解释呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.00,0:48:58.18,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the answer is, you cannot.\N{\rChinese}好？答案是，你无法解释。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.10,0:49:03.16,English,,0,0,0,,So, in foundation,\N{\rChinese}于是，在基础上，
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.56,0:49:05.94,English,,0,0,0,,okay, the solution, okay, but there is a solution to this.\N{\rChinese}好了，方案是，嗯，但确实有个方案。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.12,0:49:11.24,English,,0,0,0,,The solution is to create another organization.\N{\rChinese}方案就是再创建一个组织。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.90,0:49:14.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, remember that, technical history is an AI model.\N{\rChinese}好的，记住：技术历史是一个 AI 模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.10,0:49:16.74,English,,0,0,0,,It's basically a computer. But\N{\rChinese}它基本上是台电脑。但
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.74,0:49:20.88,English,,0,0,0,,as Eric points out, you will always have edge cases.\N{\rChinese}正如埃里克指出的，你总会有边缘案例。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.06,0:49:23.78,English,,0,0,0,,You'll always have someone appear out of nowhere.\N{\rChinese}你总会有人突然出现。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.06,0:49:25.36,English,,0,0,0,,And for whatever reason,\N{\rChinese}不管什么原因，
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.44,0:49:28.94,English,,0,0,0,,he's able to manipulate events to control\N{\rChinese}他能操纵事件来掌控。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.94,0:49:31.26,English,,0,0,0,,and direct history in his favor, okay?\N{\rChinese}并直接把历史倾向他，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.92,0:49:37.88,English,,0,0,0,,So what you do to solve this problem is you create another organization,\N{\rChinese}为了解决这个问题，你就创建另一个组织，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.28,0:49:41.94,English,,0,0,0,,okay? And in, I think, Asimov's foundation, it's called the Second Foundation.\N{\rChinese}我想在阿西莫夫的基础里，它叫第二基金会。
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.26,0:49:47.78,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the idea of the Second Foundation is\N{\rChinese}好的？第二基金会的想法是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.78,0:49:51.34,English,,0,0,0,,that there is a computer, there is the AI, okay?\N{\rChinese}有一台电脑，有一个AI，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.60,0:49:56.42,English,,0,0,0,,But behind the AI are a team of specialists\N{\rChinese}但AI背后是一支专家团队
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.62,0:50:00.82,English,,0,0,0,,who observe the AI, who observe history,\N{\rChinese}观察AI的人，观察历史的人，
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.06,0:50:04.40,English,,0,0,0,,and who correct the AI for edge cases, okay?\N{\rChinese}并且在边缘情况时修正AI的人，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.08,0:50:07.94,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So if Putin appears and is like,\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？如果普京出现并且是这样，
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.02,0:50:11.24,English,,0,0,0,,okay, well, clearly, I'm not accounting for Putin, well,\N{\rChinese}好的，显然，我没有把普京算进去，嗯，
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.28,0:50:14.52,English,,0,0,0,,then I change the equations in the AI to account for Putin, okay?\N{\rChinese}于是我在AI里改了方程，把普京算进去，嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.82,0:50:17.24,English,,0,0,0,,So this team of experts, the Second Foundation,\N{\rChinese}于是这支专家团队，第二基金会，
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.60,0:50:20.44,English,,0,0,0,,will correct the AI, right?\N{\rChinese}会修正AI，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.58,0:50:23.26,English,,0,0,0,,Now, what's interesting about the Second Foundation is\N{\rChinese}现在，第二基金会有趣的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.26,0:50:28.46,English,,0,0,0,,that these people are telepaths.\N{\rChinese}这些人是通灵者。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.06,0:50:31.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Telepaths.\N{\rChinese}好的？通灵者。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.42,0:50:34.20,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that they can read your mind.\N{\rChinese}意思是他们能读懂你的心。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.68,0:50:38.54,English,,0,0,0,,Not only can they read your mind, but they can troll your mind, okay?\N{\rChinese}不只是能读懂你的心，还能玩弄你的心，嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.12,0:50:41.70,English,,0,0,0,,So... And\N{\rChinese}于是……还有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.70,0:50:44.80,English,,0,0,0,,that's another reason why I think we're really interested in something about psychohistory.\N{\rChinese}这又是我认为我们对心理历史感兴趣的另一个原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.50,0:50:48.66,English,,0,0,0,,Like, okay, there's a promise that\N{\rChinese}比如说，嗯，有个承诺……
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.66,0:50:51.90,English,,0,0,0,,we can predict the future, but there's also a promise\N{\rChinese}我们可以预测未来，但也有一个承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.90,0:50:54.66,English,,0,0,0,,that within our minds,\N{\rChinese}在我们的心中，
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.84,0:50:57.48,English,,0,0,0,,there are some special abilities that\N{\rChinese}有一些特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.48,0:51:00.16,English,,0,0,0,,we might have the potential for, but\N{\rChinese}我们可能拥有潜力，但我们从未曾完全尝试实现。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.16,0:51:04.12,English,,0,0,0,,we never ever fully attempted to achieve.\N{\rChinese}好的？这有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.72,0:51:07.16,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好的？这有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.82,0:51:10.42,English,,0,0,0,,And is it possible in the future\N{\rChinese}并且未来可否出现通灵者？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.42,0:51:13.96,English,,0,0,0,,that telepaths will arrive I think yes.\N{\rChinese}我认为会出现。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.08,0:51:16.52,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is that you can make the argument that\N{\rChinese}答案是你可以这样论证。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.52,0:51:21.00,English,,0,0,0,,these edge cases that Eric refers to, these great men of history,\N{\rChinese}这些边缘案例，埃里克提到的历史伟人，
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.08,0:51:23.52,English,,0,0,0,,they're actually telepaths.\N{\rChinese}他们实际上是通灵者。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.42,0:51:26.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? They're actually telepaths.\N{\rChinese}好的吗？这有道理吗？他们实际上是通灵者。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.82,0:51:31.12,English,,0,0,0,,So someone like Putin, why is Putin able to do what he does?\N{\rChinese}那么像普京这样的人，为什么他能做到他所做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.62,0:51:33.04,English,,0,0,0,,And you can make the argument, like,\N{\rChinese}你可以这样论证，像是，
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.10,0:51:37.42,English,,0,0,0,,he has almost some telepathic abilities,\N{\rChinese}他几乎拥有某种通灵能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.78,0:51:40.36,English,,0,0,0,,okay? He can read other people's minds.\N{\rChinese}好的？他能读懂别人的心思。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.52,0:51:42.04,English,,0,0,0,,He can troll other people's minds.\N{\rChinese}他能把别人的心思玩弄。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.04,0:51:44.92,English,,0,0,0,,How else can you explain that someone\N{\rChinese}还有什么办法解释这样的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.92,0:51:47.38,English,,0,0,0,,who does not come\N{\rChinese}谁没来自特殊背景，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.02,0:51:50.00,English,,0,0,0,,from a special background, right?\N{\rChinese}他不是俄罗斯精英之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.06,0:51:51.62,English,,0,0,0,,He's not of the Russian elite.\N{\rChinese}He's not of theRussian elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.44,0:51:56.62,English,,0,0,0,,But he's able to amass so much power\N{\rChinese}但他能在短短几十年内独自积聚如此多的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.40,0:52:00.52,English,,0,0,0,,all by himself in only a few decades\N{\rChinese}只靠自己在仅仅几十年间就做到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.32,0:52:05.18,English,,0,0,0,,so that today, he's basically the emperor of Russia.\N{\rChinese}于是今天，他基本上就是俄罗斯的皇帝。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.38,0:52:09.00,English,,0,0,0,,And all of Russia heeds his command.\N{\rChinese}俄国一切都听从他的指挥。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.38,0:52:11.92,English,,0,0,0,,Russia just moves the way that he wants it to move.\N{\rChinese}俄国只按他所愿的方向运转。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.92,0:52:14.32,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So you can make the argument that\N{\rChinese}好？于是你可以这样论证。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.32,0:52:17.94,English,,0,0,0,,Putin is almost a telepath.\N{\rChinese}普京几乎是个通灵者。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.66,0:52:20.94,English,,0,0,0,,And is it possible\N{\rChinese}而且可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.60,0:52:24.44,English,,0,0,0,,that in the future we'll have more telepaths?\N{\rChinese}未来我们会有更多通灵者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.90,0:52:27.22,English,,0,0,0,,And we can, over time,\N{\rChinese}我们也可以，随着时间的推移，
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.34,0:52:30.62,English,,0,0,0,,harness the power of these telepaths\N{\rChinese}利用这些通灵者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.96,0:52:36.42,English,,0,0,0,,to create the second foundation and to control psychohistory?\N{\rChinese}来打造第二个基础并掌控心理史
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.32,0:52:40.26,English,,0,0,0,,Possibly, right? Okay?\N{\rChinese}可能吧？好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.36,0:52:43.20,English,,0,0,0,,Because, like, how else would we explain great men, okay?\N{\rChinese}因为，像，怎么解释伟人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.18,0:52:48.52,English,,0,0,0,,You look at someone like Homer and Dante, right?\N{\rChinese}你看像荷马和但丁的人，吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.86,0:52:52.70,English,,0,0,0,,The only explanation that you can have for Homer and Dante is\N{\rChinese}对荷马和但丁的唯一解释是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.60,0:52:58.00,English,,0,0,0,,they were... They had God -given gifts, okay?\N{\rChinese}他们是……他们拥有上帝赐予的天赋，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.06,0:52:59.52,English,,0,0,0,,Or maybe God was speaking to them.\N{\rChinese}或者上帝正对他们说话。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.64,0:53:01.52,English,,0,0,0,,Or maybe they were just speaking for God.\N{\rChinese}或者他们只是为上帝发言。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.92,0:53:05.36,English,,0,0,0,,Right? That's the only explanation that you can have for Homer\N{\rChinese}对吗？这就是你能给荷马的唯一解释。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.36,0:53:08.02,English,,0,0,0,,and Dante because they so\N{\rChinese}以及但丁，因为他们如此
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.02,0:53:10.74,English,,0,0,0,,clearly stepped out of history and directed history.\N{\rChinese}清晰地从历史中跳出来并指引历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.06,0:53:13.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, does that make sense? Okay?\N{\rChinese}好的，这有道理吗？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.92,0:53:16.68,English,,0,0,0,,But thanks for the question, Eric.\N{\rChinese}谢谢你的问题，埃里克。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.88,0:53:18.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So edge cases are great men\N{\rChinese}好的？边缘情况就是伟人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.52,0:53:23.30,English,,0,0,0,,who appear now and then, and you cannot ever predict these people.\N{\rChinese}他们时不时出现，你永远预测不到这些人。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.02,0:53:26.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好的？还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.38,0:53:31.66,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. This...\N{\rChinese}好的。这个……
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:33.72,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Yes? Yes, Celine?\N{\rChinese}嗯？是吗？是的，塞琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.28,0:53:35.76,English,,0,0,0,,..\N{\rChinese}……
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.66,0:53:40.14,English,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a great question, okay?\N{\rChinese}哦，那是个很好的问题，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.24,0:53:44.66,English,,0,0,0,,Um, okay. How do you model\N{\rChinese}嗯，好。你是怎么建模的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.82,0:53:48.92,English,,0,0,0,,love, learn, and create, okay?\N{\rChinese}爱、学、创，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.86,0:53:52.76,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is that\N{\rChinese}答案是这样：
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.38,0:53:55.26,English,,0,0,0,,there has to be a certain amount of\N{\rChinese}必须有一定量的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.84,0:53:58.68,English,,0,0,0,,autonomy or agency\N{\rChinese}自主或能动性
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.62,0:54:03.24,English,,0,0,0,,in the lives of people.\N{\rChinese}在人的生活中。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.24,0:54:05.88,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? What we call freedom and liberty.\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？我们所说的自由和自由度。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.26,0:54:11.00,English,,0,0,0,,Because if you have freedom and liberty, then you're able to do what you want.\N{\rChinese}因为如果你拥有自由和自由度，你就能做你想做的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.32,0:54:14.06,English,,0,0,0,,And what you want to do is love,\N{\rChinese}而你想做的就是爱，
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.28,0:54:16.70,English,,0,0,0,,um, create, and...\N{\rChinese}嗯，创造，和……
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.24,0:54:18.68,English,,0,0,0,,and grow, okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}然后成长，好吗？这通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.04,0:54:22.18,English,,0,0,0,,So you need to model, um, agency\N{\rChinese}所以你需要把主体性建模
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.18,0:54:25.34,English,,0,0,0,,and freedom into the structure, okay?\N{\rChinese}并把自由放进结构里，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.76,0:54:27.76,English,,0,0,0,,The second thing is, um,\N{\rChinese}第二点是，嗯，
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.88,0:54:33.18,English,,0,0,0,,social interaction. Okay?\N{\rChinese}社会互动，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.18,0:54:38.02,English,,0,0,0,,In other words, the more we're able to interact with each other,\N{\rChinese}换句话说，越能互相交流，
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.88,0:54:42.08,English,,0,0,0,,the more we're willing to love,\N{\rChinese}我们就越愿意去爱。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.76,0:54:44.30,English,,0,0,0,,create, and grow.\N{\rChinese}创造，并成长。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.50,0:54:46.70,English,,0,0,0,,Because these powers come from others, right?\N{\rChinese}因为这些力量来自他人，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.88,0:54:49.34,English,,0,0,0,,You can't love yourself. You have to love someone else.\N{\rChinese}你不能自爱，你得去爱别人。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.90,0:54:51.32,English,,0,0,0,,You can't create by yourself.\N{\rChinese}你自己做不到创造。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.50,0:54:54.22,English,,0,0,0,,You have to create in a group, okay? And you can't learn by yourself.\N{\rChinese}你得在团队里做，行吗？你也不能单独学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.34,0:54:56.52,English,,0,0,0,,You have to learn from others. Okay?\N{\rChinese}你得向别人学习，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.60,0:55:00.80,English,,0,0,0,,So you also have to model in, um, as much group interaction as possible.\N{\rChinese}所以你也得尽量多做小组互动。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.70,0:55:04.42,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And the last thing is\N{\rChinese}好吧？最后一点是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.02,0:55:07.76,English,,0,0,0,,you also have to model in the idea of compassion.\N{\rChinese}你还得把“同情”这个概念融进去。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.88,0:55:15.96,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So the idea here is that, um,\N{\rChinese}好的？所以这里的想法是，呃，
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.48,0:55:21.58,English,,0,0,0,,if I all put you on an island together,\N{\rChinese}如果我把你们全部放在同一座岛上，
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.48,0:55:24.14,English,,0,0,0,,okay, and you must survive,\N{\rChinese}好了，你们必须要生存下来。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.94,0:55:28.42,English,,0,0,0,,well, you will become compassionate with each other,\N{\rChinese}好了，你们会彼此产生同情，
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.54,0:55:30.22,English,,0,0,0,,because that's the only way to survive, right?\N{\rChinese}因为那是唯一能生存下去的办法，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.98,0:55:35.16,English,,0,0,0,,But, if I put you guys into a bank,\N{\rChinese}不过，如果我把你们放进银行，
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.40,0:55:38.42,English,,0,0,0,,and I say to you that\N{\rChinese}我跟你们说，如果你们赚了一百万，我再给你们两百万，谁赚得最多，我就送一辆法拉利，猜猜谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.42,0:55:41.82,English,,0,0,0,,if you make a million dollars, and I give you two million dollars,\N{\rChinese}我跟你们说，如果你们赚了一百万，我再给你们两百万，谁赚得最多，我就送一辆法拉利，猜猜谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.96,0:55:45.86,English,,0,0,0,,whoever makes the most money, I will give a Ferrari to, guess what, guys?\N{\rChinese}我跟你们说，如果你们赚了一百万，我再给你们两百万，谁赚得最多，我就送一辆法拉利，猜猜谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.14,0:55:48.66,English,,0,0,0,,You will all hate each other.\N{\rChinese}你们会互相仇恨。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.82,0:55:50.56,English,,0,0,0,,You will all want to kill each other, okay?\N{\rChinese}你们会互相想杀了，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.08,0:55:52.52,English,,0,0,0,,You understand? So\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.52,0:55:56.78,English,,0,0,0,,this model also has to factor in compassion.\N{\rChinese}这个模型还要考虑同情。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.12,0:55:59.36,English,,0,0,0,,How compassionate is this society?\N{\rChinese}这个社会有多同情？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.50,0:56:02.78,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Because if you have compassion,\N{\rChinese}好吧？因为有同情的话，
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.20,0:56:04.92,English,,0,0,0,,then people are willing to work together.\N{\rChinese}然后人们愿意一起工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.14,0:56:09.90,English,,0,0,0,,If people are willing to work together, then people will have the greater capacity to love, create, and grow.\N{\rChinese}如果人们愿意一起工作，那么他们就会有更大的能力去爱、创造和成长。
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.32,0:56:11.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好吧？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.24,0:56:16.18,English,,0,0,0,,Actually, guys, we have all these theories.\N{\rChinese}实际上，伙计们，我们有这么多理论。
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.98,0:56:19.02,English,,0,0,0,,It's just like no one's turned this into a mathematical model,\N{\rChinese}就像没有人把它们变成社会的数学模型一样，
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.78,0:56:23.20,English,,0,0,0,,okay, for society. Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好了，接着说。
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.46,0:56:35.94,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah? .\N{\rChinese}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.60,0:56:52.44,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so\N{\rChinese}嗯，好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.44,0:56:54.88,English,,0,0,0,,Eric asked a question,\N{\rChinese}埃里克提了个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.26,0:56:57.58,English,,0,0,0,,is it possible to\N{\rChinese}它可否完全理解人类行为与动机？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.58,0:57:01.84,English,,0,0,0,,completely understand human behavior and motivation?\N{\rChinese}还有两种不同的方式来观察这个问题，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.96,0:57:09.10,English,,0,0,0,,And there are two different ways of looking at the issue, okay?\N{\rChinese}And there are two different ways of looking at the issue, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.10,0:57:14.82,English,,0,0,0,,The first way is to use a social science approach,\N{\rChinese}第一种方法是采用社会科学的视角，
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.00,0:57:16.86,English,,0,0,0,,okay? So you look at economics, psychology,\N{\rChinese}好吧？于是你会去研究经济学、心理学，
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.36,0:57:19.80,English,,0,0,0,,anthropology, sociology, right?\N{\rChinese}人类学、社会学，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.98,0:57:21.02,English,,0,0,0,,What are they trying to do?\N{\rChinese}他们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.14,0:57:26.02,English,,0,0,0,,They're trying to figure out mathematically\N{\rChinese}他们正试图用数学方法弄清楚是什么驱动我们，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.54,0:57:28.14,English,,0,0,0,,what drives us, okay?\N{\rChinese}他们正试图用数学方法弄清楚是什么驱动我们，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.14,0:57:29.74,English,,0,0,0,,You understand?\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.10,0:57:31.38,English,,0,0,0,,But there's another approach.\N{\rChinese}但还有另一种方法。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.60,0:57:33.30,English,,0,0,0,,It's called the literature approach,\N{\rChinese}它叫做文学方法。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.04,0:57:38.48,English,,0,0,0,,which is that we can't actually quantify\N{\rChinese}这就是我们无法真正量化的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.70,0:57:44.30,English,,0,0,0,,or explain human behavior, okay?\N{\rChinese}或者解释人类行为，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.98,0:57:49.74,English,,0,0,0,,But there are truths that can be expressed in literature.\N{\rChinese}但有些真理可以用文学来表达。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.42,0:57:53.56,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好的？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.76,0:57:58.00,English,,0,0,0,,So think about the very first book we read, The Iliad.\N{\rChinese}那么想想我们刚读的第一本书，伊利亚德。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.14,0:58:01.84,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Where\N{\rChinese}对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.84,0:58:05.08,English,,0,0,0,,Achilles has killed Hector and Prime wants the body back.\N{\rChinese}阿基琉斯杀死赫克托尔，普莱姆想取回尸体。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.26,0:58:08.76,English,,0,0,0,,So Prime sneaks into Achilles' tent and kisses his hand,\N{\rChinese}于是普莱姆潜入阿基琉斯帐篷，吻了他的手，右吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.34,0:58:10.78,English,,0,0,0,,right? That moment.\N{\rChinese}那一刻。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.34,0:58:14.14,English,,0,0,0,,You can never mathematically express it.\N{\rChinese}可以用数学表达不了。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.22,0:58:15.76,English,,0,0,0,,You can only write about it.\N{\rChinese}只能写出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.14,0:58:18.52,English,,0,0,0,,But think about how much truth and power\N{\rChinese}但想想其中蕴含的真理与力量。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.40,0:58:21.08,English,,0,0,0,,is in that one scene.\N{\rChinese}在那一幕里。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.98,0:58:26.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense, Eric?\N{\rChinese}好吧？这样说通吗，埃里克？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.60,0:58:29.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So again, I think someone like Homer\N{\rChinese}好吧？所以，我想像荷马那样的人会是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.86,0:58:32.42,English,,0,0,0,,and Dante,\N{\rChinese}而且但丁，
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.00,0:58:38.70,English,,0,0,0,,their mission is to express to us,\N{\rChinese}他们的使命是向我们表达，
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.72,0:58:41.46,English,,0,0,0,,in the most beautiful way, the human truths, okay?\N{\rChinese}以最美的方式，呈现人类真理，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.68,0:58:43.04,English,,0,0,0,,Like what drives us.\N{\rChinese}像推动我们的那样。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.36,0:58:44.74,English,,0,0,0,,And Dante is very explicit.\N{\rChinese}而但丁则非常明确。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.88,0:58:48.52,English,,0,0,0,,He says that what drives us is love\N{\rChinese}他说推动我们的就是爱。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.52,0:58:50.62,English,,0,0,0,,and the willingness to imagine, okay?\N{\rChinese}并且愿意去想象，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.76,0:58:53.48,English,,0,0,0,,That's who we are. If we love, we'll be more human.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们。若我们爱，我们更有人性。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.62,0:58:55.72,English,,0,0,0,,If we imagine, we'll be more human, okay?\N{\rChinese}若我们想象，我们更有人性，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.72,0:58:58.56,English,,0,0,0,,And that's really the argument I make as well.\N{\rChinese}而这正是我所提出的论点。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.84,0:59:00.32,English,,0,0,0,,All right? And that\N{\rChinese}好了？而且这点是……】
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.32,0:59:03.08,English,,0,0,0,,has to be the underlying truth\N{\rChinese}】
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.08,0:59:07.58,English,,0,0,0,,of whatever AI model you create, okay?\N{\rChinese}无论你创建的AI模型是什么，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.94,0:59:14.78,English,,0,0,0,,All right? Any more questions? Yeah?\N{\rChinese}好了？还有问题吗？嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.80,0:59:22.96,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay.\N{\rChinese}好的。好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.24,0:59:26.46,English,,0,0,0,,So, Celine asked a great question.\N{\rChinese}于是，塞琳提出了一个很好的问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.58,0:59:28.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, if it says that\N{\rChinese}好的，嗯，如果它说我们想要爱、创造和成长，那为什么我们最终会自我毁灭？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.86,0:59:33.58,English,,0,0,0,,we want to love, create, and grow, then why do we end up destroying ourselves?\N{\rChinese}we want to love, create, and grow, thenwhy do we end up destroying ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.18,0:59:37.70,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is that love\N{\rChinese}而答案是，爱与恨是一股力量。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.70,0:59:41.88,English,,0,0,0,,and hate are one force.\N{\rChinese}你明白吗？如果我不能爱你，我就会恨你。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.16,0:59:46.10,English,,0,0,0,,You understand? If I can't love you, I'm going to hate you.\N{\rChinese}You understand? If I can't love you, I'm going to hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.58,0:59:48.90,English,,0,0,0,,You understand, okay? Guess what, guys?\N{\rChinese}你明白吗，好吗？猜猜，大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.46,0:59:53.38,English,,0,0,0,,Creation and destruction are two different things. Destruction is one force as well.\N{\rChinese}创造与毁灭是两件事。毁灭也是一种力量。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.58,0:59:55.92,English,,0,0,0,,If I can't create, then I want to destroy\N{\rChinese}如果我不能创造，那我就想毁灭。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.92,1:00:00.36,English,,0,0,0,,because my need for creation can't be satisfied.\N{\rChinese}因为我的创造需求未能得到满足。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.80,1:00:04.18,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So, a society\N{\rChinese}这样说有道理吗？于是，一个社会
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.18,1:00:07.94,English,,0,0,0,,that nurtures our willingness to love\N{\rChinese}培养我们愿意去爱的意愿。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.94,1:00:10.36,English,,0,0,0,,and create and grow, like the Greeks,\N{\rChinese}并且创造并成长，像古希腊人一样，
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.58,1:00:12.98,English,,0,0,0,,will flourish, okay?\N{\rChinese}将会繁荣，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.36,1:00:16.14,English,,0,0,0,,But eventually, you reach a point where\N{\rChinese}但最终，你会到达一个点
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.14,1:00:19.78,English,,0,0,0,,the elite have amassed power.\N{\rChinese}精英已聚集力量。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.68,1:00:23.88,English,,0,0,0,,They've centralized and consolidated power, and so\N{\rChinese}他们已集中并巩固力量，随后……
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.88,1:00:28.50,English,,0,0,0,,they want to turn everyone\N{\rChinese}于是他们想让所有人……
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.50,1:00:30.06,English,,0,0,0,,else into basically a slave.\N{\rChinese}变成基本的奴隶。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.66,1:00:32.92,English,,0,0,0,,When you're a slave, you can't love.\N{\rChinese}当你是奴隶时，你就不能爱。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.16,1:00:34.66,English,,0,0,0,,You can't create. You can't learn.\N{\rChinese}你不能创造，也不能学习。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.76,1:00:37.78,English,,0,0,0,,You can't grow. Therefore, you rebel, and you destroy the society.\N{\rChinese}你无法成长。因此，你会反叛，并摧毁社会。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.28,1:00:40.44,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? Okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？这样说通吗？好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.08,1:00:45.98,English,,0,0,0,,But, again, the fundamental human need are these three things,\N{\rChinese}但，再次说，人的基本需求是这三件事，
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.08,1:00:50.02,English,,0,0,0,,but within each of these things is another force.\N{\rChinese}但在这些事物之中又有另一股力量。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.86,1:00:54.20,English,,0,0,0,,And if love can't express itself, then hate will express itself.\N{\rChinese}如果爱无法表达，恰好恨便会表达。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.74,1:00:57.60,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay?\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.88,1:01:01.72,English,,0,0,0,,All right. Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好的。还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.98,1:01:05.78,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah?.\N{\rChinese}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.66,1:01:16.52,English,,0,0,0,,... .\N{\rChinese}……
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.08,1:01:27.02,English,,0,0,0,,. So, Sally asked a great question, which is, like, who\N{\rChinese}. 所以，萨莉问了一个很好的问题，就是，呃，谁
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.02,1:01:29.62,English,,0,0,0,,would control this AI?\N{\rChinese}会控制这台 AI 吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.88,1:01:32.84,English,,0,0,0,,And how can we ensure that\N{\rChinese}那我们怎么确保呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.84,1:01:37.10,English,,0,0,0,,this AI is not exploited by the\N{\rChinese}这台 AI 不是被……
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.10,1:01:41.06,English,,0,0,0,,elite in order to justify their corruption and cruelty, okay?\N{\rChinese}精英们用来证明他们的腐败与残暴，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.06,1:01:44.62,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer has to be\N{\rChinese}而答案必须是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.62,1:01:48.28,English,,0,0,0,,really the second foundation, okay?\N{\rChinese}真正是第二个基石，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.70,1:01:51.92,English,,0,0,0,,Basically, a group of scholars,\N{\rChinese}基本上，一群学者，
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.06,1:01:54.50,English,,0,0,0,,academics, experts, who\N{\rChinese}学者、专家、专业人士，
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.50,1:01:57.74,English,,0,0,0,,dedicate themselves to this AI, okay?\N{\rChinese}致力于这台 AI，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.46,1:02:02.16,English,,0,0,0,,And this AI, the other thing is that it has to be open and transparent.\N{\rChinese}这台 AI，另一件事是它必须开放透明。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.64,1:02:06.14,English,,0,0,0,,That's why it's so hard to build, right?\N{\rChinese}这就是它构建之难的原因，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.98,1:02:09.16,English,,0,0,0,,It has to be open and transparent.\N{\rChinese}它必须开放透明。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.98,1:02:12.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? If it's open and transparent, then\N{\rChinese}好的？如果它是开放透明的，大家就得同意这台 AI 将用于好事，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.76,1:02:15.80,English,,0,0,0,,everyone has to agree that this AI is going to be used for good, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？如果它是开放透明的，大家就得同意这台 AI 将用于好事，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.10,1:02:20.10,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that what this AI does is you can ask it different questions,\N{\rChinese}意思是这台 AI 的工作是你可以问它不同的问题，
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.24,1:02:22.74,English,,0,0,0,,and it will give you different scenarios.\N{\rChinese}它会给你不同的情景。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.14,1:02:26.52,English,,0,0,0,,And we can all agree on which scenario we want,\N{\rChinese}我们可以一起决定想要哪一个情景。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.04,1:02:30.40,English,,0,0,0,,and therefore we can agree on what action to take, okay?\N{\rChinese}于是我们就能就采取什么行动达成一致，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.06,1:02:34.66,English,,0,0,0,,So this AI has to be part of a democratic system\N{\rChinese}所以这台 AI 必须成为民主体系的一部分
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.66,1:02:36.20,English,,0,0,0,,where everyone is involved.\N{\rChinese}其中每个人都参与其中
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.20,1:02:39.22,English,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, as Sally points out,\N{\rChinese}否则，正如萨莉所指出的，
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.32,1:02:41.44,English,,0,0,0,,it can only be abused,\N{\rChinese}它只能被滥用，
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.80,1:02:47.44,English,,0,0,0,,okay? It can only be used to oppress others,\N{\rChinese}好吗？它只能用来压迫别人。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.72,1:02:49.12,English,,0,0,0,,okay?\N{\rChinese}好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.28,1:02:52.30,English,,0,0,0,,But the point of this AI is that\N{\rChinese}但这台 AI 的要点是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.30,1:02:55.28,English,,0,0,0,,it gives us a platform\N{\rChinese}它给我们一个平台
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.28,1:02:59.78,English,,0,0,0,,as humans to agree on certain actions\N{\rChinese}作为人类，我们需要就某些行动达成共识
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.78,1:03:02.72,English,,0,0,0,,that we must stick together, okay?\N{\rChinese}我们必须团结一致，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.50,1:03:07.08,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? So for example, we can all agree\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？举个例子，我们都能同意
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.08,1:03:09.48,English,,0,0,0,,that climate change is bad.\N{\rChinese}气候变化是坏事。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.66,1:03:11.96,English,,0,0,0,,We can all agree that war is bad, right?\N{\rChinese}我们都能同意战争是坏事。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.48,1:03:16.40,English,,0,0,0,,But this AI will actually give us solutions to these problems\N{\rChinese}这台 AI 实际上会给我们这些问题的解决方案。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.40,1:03:19.50,English,,0,0,0,,because this AI can map out the future for us.\N{\rChinese}因为这台 AI 能为我们绘制未来。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.02,1:03:21.70,English,,0,0,0,,And AI will say, well, listen,\N{\rChinese}而 AI 会说，好吧，听着，
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.84,1:03:25.84,English,,0,0,0,,if the United States intervenes in Ukraine,\N{\rChinese}如果美国介入乌克兰，
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.08,1:03:27.84,English,,0,0,0,,then this will happen, right?\N{\rChinese}然后这件事就会发生，没错吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.06,1:03:30.34,English,,0,0,0,,The United States attacks Iran, then this will happen.\N{\rChinese}美国攻击伊朗后，这件事就会发生。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.82,1:03:35.62,English,,0,0,0,,And that becomes a very powerful argument for correct\N{\rChinese}于是这就成为了一个很有力的论据。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.62,1:03:38.18,English,,0,0,0,,and proper behavior, okay?\N{\rChinese}并且正确的行为，好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.60,1:03:40.70,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? All right.\N{\rChinese}这样说通吗？全部好。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.74,1:03:42.36,English,,0,0,0,,But again, guys,\N{\rChinese}但再说一次，伙计们。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.76,1:03:44.64,English,,0,0,0,,this is just conjecture, okay?\N{\rChinese}这只是推测，好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.82,1:03:46.16,English,,0,0,0,,And I've already said this.\N{\rChinese}我已经说过了。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.36,1:03:50.36,English,,0,0,0,,It's going to take at least 50 to 100 years to build this AI,\N{\rChinese}要建成这个AI至少要50到100年。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.00,1:03:53.98,English,,0,0,0,,and you will be up against tremendous opposition,\N{\rChinese}并且你将面临巨大的对抗，好的？史学家们会喜欢这件事的。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.40,1:03:58.44,English,,0,0,0,,right? Historians aren't going to like this.\N{\rChinese}精英们会喜欢这件事的，好的？】
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.62,1:04:01.82,English,,0,0,0,,The elite aren't going to like this, right?\N{\rChinese}\}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.10,1:04:08.80,English,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, we have to remember, like, guess what?\N{\rChinese}但与此同时，我们要记住，呃，猜怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.64,1:04:12.96,English,,0,0,0,,Homer, I'm pretty sure if Homer\N{\rChinese}荷马，我很确定如果荷马
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.96,1:04:17.60,English,,0,0,0,,were living in a centralized society,\N{\rChinese}居住在一个集中的社会里，
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.54,1:04:20.38,English,,0,0,0,,the elite would be opposed to him, okay?\N{\rChinese}精英们会对他有反对，好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.44,1:04:24.44,English,,0,0,0,,Because he was making fun of very famous Greeks,\N{\rChinese}因为他在嘲笑非常著名的希腊人，好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.54,1:04:26.78,English,,0,0,0,,like Achilles and Menelaus and Agamemnon, right?\N{\rChinese}比如阿基里斯、梅涅拉俄斯和阿伽门农，好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.94,1:04:29.66,English,,0,0,0,,He was making fun of these guys. Well, guess what?\N{\rChinese}他在嘲笑这些人。好了，猜怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.88,1:04:32.84,English,,0,0,0,,When Homer's writing, society had collapsed, right?\N{\rChinese}当荷马写作时，社会已经崩溃，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.24,1:04:35.48,English,,0,0,0,,When Dante was writing, society had collapsed.\N{\rChinese}当但丁写作时，社会已经崩溃。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.76,1:04:41.92,English,,0,0,0,,So if it is true, if my predictions are correct\N{\rChinese}如果这是真的，如果我的预测正确
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.92,1:04:43.78,English,,0,0,0,,and society is approaching collapse,\N{\rChinese}社会正接近崩溃
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.14,1:04:47.04,English,,0,0,0,,then there should be a lot of space and leeway\N{\rChinese}那就会有很多空间和余地
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.04,1:04:49.36,English,,0,0,0,,and flexibility to create this AI, okay?\N{\rChinese}并且有灵活性来创造这AI，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.34,1:04:54.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好的。还有别的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.68,1:04:57.30,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah?.\N{\rChinese}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.60,1:05:02.86,English,,0,0,0,,That's a great question.\N{\rChinese}这是个很好的问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.44,1:05:08.08,English,,0,0,0,,So won't different people, different nations want different outcomes?\N{\rChinese}所以不同的人、不同的国家会想要不同的结果吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.40,1:05:12.48,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is yeah. Like, if you are alive today,\N{\rChinese}答案是的。比如说，如果你今天还活着，
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.58,1:05:14.20,English,,0,0,0,,if you're America, you want America to be a hegemon.\N{\rChinese}如果你是美国人，你想让美国成为霸权。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.42,1:05:16.38,English,,0,0,0,,If you're Putin, you want Russia to be the hegemon.\N{\rChinese}如果你是普京，你想让俄罗斯成为霸权。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.66,1:05:18.80,English,,0,0,0,,If you're China, you want China to be the hegemon, right?\N{\rChinese}如果你是中国人，你想让中国成为霸权，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.92,1:05:21.32,English,,0,0,0,,You want different outcomes. So\N{\rChinese}你想要不同的结果。所以
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.32,1:05:23.16,English,,0,0,0,,my argument is that\N{\rChinese}我的论点是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.16,1:05:26.98,English,,0,0,0,,the structure of society today is not sustainable.\N{\rChinese}今天社会的结构不再可持续。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.34,1:05:29.10,English,,0,0,0,,Everything's going to collapse. And\N{\rChinese}一切都将崩溃。然后
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.10,1:05:32.54,English,,0,0,0,,we are going to transition from a\N{\rChinese}我们将从约八十亿人过渡到一十亿人。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.54,1:05:36.42,English,,0,0,0,,population of about 8 billion people to a population of 1 billion people.\N{\rChinese}population of about 8 billion peopleto a population of 1 billion people.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.94,1:05:39.82,English,,0,0,0,,And when you have 1 billion people and,\N{\rChinese}当你拥有一亿人口时，
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.98,1:05:43.06,English,,0,0,0,,like, there's no place to grow crops,\N{\rChinese}比如说，没有地方种植被子，
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.26,1:05:46.58,English,,0,0,0,,and pollution is everywhere,\N{\rChinese}而且污染无处不在。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.84,1:05:49.54,English,,0,0,0,,and war is everywhere, guess what happens?\N{\rChinese}战争无处不在，猜猜会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.46,1:05:53.34,English,,0,0,0,,Humans are united in their goals,\N{\rChinese}人类在目标上已统一，
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.58,1:05:56.56,English,,0,0,0,,which is basically how do we create a better civilization,\N{\rChinese}这基本就是我们如何创造更好文明的方式。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.98,1:05:58.58,English,,0,0,0,,okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好的？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.78,1:06:02.02,English,,0,0,0,,When all of a sudden it's collapsed, everyone's like, how do we recreate civilization?\N{\rChinese}突然间全局崩溃，大家都在问：我们怎样重建文明？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.68,1:06:07.26,English,,0,0,0,,That's the goal. But in a more progressive, more democratic,\N{\rChinese}这就是目标。但要更进步、更民主的方式。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.88,1:06:09.50,English,,0,0,0,,and more prosperous way.\N{\rChinese}更繁荣的方式。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.60,1:06:12.16,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's what I'm betting on.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是我下注的。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.30,1:06:15.10,English,,0,0,0,,But I don't know, okay? And again,\N{\rChinese}但我不知道，好的？再说一次，
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.56,1:06:22.18,English,,0,0,0,,if everyone's fighting over the AI, this AI cannot be created, okay?\N{\rChinese}如果大家都在争夺这AI，它就无法被创造，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.52,1:06:27.16,English,,0,0,0,,Because different people will want this AI to be biased in a different way.\N{\rChinese}因为不同的人会想让这AI偏向各自的立场。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.32,1:06:32.40,English,,0,0,0,,This AI can only work if it steps outside of history\N{\rChinese}这AI只有在脱离历史后才能运作。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.40,1:06:35.72,English,,0,0,0,,and steps outside of human interests, okay?\N{\rChinese}并且脱离人类利益，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.90,1:06:39.90,English,,0,0,0,,If it's speaking for all of humanity rather than one nation or one group of people.\N{\rChinese}它若能代表全人类而非单一民族或单一群体发声。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.32,1:06:45.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好？还有别问吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.24,1:06:48.72,English,,0,0,0,,Is this clear to you guys?\N{\rChinese}这对你们来说清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.48,1:06:51.70,English,,0,0,0,,Alright. So, um...\N{\rChinese}好的。那么，嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.36,1:06:55.82,English,,0,0,0,,Alright. So, this is the very end,\N{\rChinese}好的。那么，这就是最后了。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.98,1:06:59.76,English,,0,0,0,,and I'll spend, like, five more minutes to talk about\N{\rChinese}我会再花大约五分钟来聊聊今年，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.22,1:07:02.92,English,,0,0,0,,this year, okay?\N{\rChinese}好吧，嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.20,1:07:05.38,English,,0,0,0,,So, um...\N{\rChinese}So, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.38,1:07:10.12,English,,0,0,0,,This is the very first time I've taught both courses, okay?\N{\rChinese}这可是我第一次同时教授这两门课程，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.28,1:07:13.70,English,,0,0,0,,In the first semester, we read the great books.\N{\rChinese}在第一学期，我们阅读了这些经典书籍。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.42,1:07:17.76,English,,0,0,0,,And... Um...\N{\rChinese}然后……嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.32,1:07:20.26,English,,0,0,0,,I was blown away\N{\rChinese}我被你们的热情所震撼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.26,1:07:25.24,English,,0,0,0,,by how much you guys enjoyed the great books. And\N{\rChinese}我被你们对这些经典书籍的喜爱所震撼。并且
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.24,1:07:30.84,English,,0,0,0,,how much you benefit from reading the great books,\N{\rChinese}你们通过阅读这些经典书籍获得的收益
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.00,1:07:35.16,English,,0,0,0,,okay? And quite honestly, I don't think anyone has tried this before.\N{\rChinese}好的？说实话，我觉得之前没人尝试过。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.10,1:07:38.30,English,,0,0,0,,Um... I know there are great books courses in university,\N{\rChinese}嗯……我知道大学里有经典书籍课程，
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.18,1:07:40.76,English,,0,0,0,,but not at the pace\N{\rChinese}但节奏不一样。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.64,1:07:43.62,English,,0,0,0,,that we had,\N{\rChinese}我们曾经得过的那样，
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.16,1:07:46.94,English,,0,0,0,,and certainly not at the level of difficulty that we had, okay?\N{\rChinese}而且肯定不如我们之前的难度，好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.18,1:07:51.62,English,,0,0,0,,So you guys should be proud of yourself, because the great books courses was very hard.\N{\rChinese}所以你们应该为自己感到自豪，因为经典书籍课程非常艰难。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.04,1:07:54.22,English,,0,0,0,,And, um... You enjoyed it.\N{\rChinese}嗯……你们玩得很开心。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.22,1:07:57.40,English,,0,0,0,,Um... Even today, most of you really like the Iliad, right?\N{\rChinese}嗯……今天你们大多数人还是很喜欢《伊利亚特》吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.60,1:08:00.56,English,,0,0,0,,You guys still remember the Iliad and think very highly of it, okay?\N{\rChinese}你们还记得《伊利亚特》，并且评价很高，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.08,1:08:02.54,English,,0,0,0,,Um... So, so...\N{\rChinese}嗯……所以，嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.54,1:08:04.32,English,,0,0,0,,So that's very impressive, so thank you.\N{\rChinese}所以这很令人印象，感谢你。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.52,1:08:07.88,English,,0,0,0,,This semester is also a new course, where\N{\rChinese}本学期也是一门新课程，
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.88,1:08:09.70,English,,0,0,0,,we looked at geopolitics.\N{\rChinese}我们看了地缘政治。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.24,1:08:12.88,English,,0,0,0,,And, um... I'm...\N{\rChinese}嗯……我……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.88,1:08:15.14,English,,0,0,0,,I'm also very impressed\N{\rChinese}我也很印象。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.18,1:08:18.58,English,,0,0,0,,by how much you've grown as well\N{\rChinese}你们成长了多少，已在这门课中。嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.20,1:08:21.54,English,,0,0,0,,in this course. Um...\N{\rChinese}你们的思考方式更为逻辑。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.22,1:08:24.20,English,,0,0,0,,The way you guys think, it's much more logical.\N{\rChinese}The way you guys think,it's much more logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.22,1:08:25.54,English,,0,0,0,,Much more analytical.\N{\rChinese}更具分析性。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.80,1:08:27.54,English,,0,0,0,,You guys are asking great questions, okay?\N{\rChinese}你们提出了很好的问题，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.74,1:08:29.12,English,,0,0,0,,So, um...\N{\rChinese}嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.12,1:08:31.50,English,,0,0,0,,Thank you again, because...\N{\rChinese}再次感谢你们，因为……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.50,1:08:36.24,English,,0,0,0,,You don't have to work hard in this course, but you chose to work hard.\N{\rChinese}你们在这门课里不必费劲，但你们选择了努力。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.46,1:08:40.27,English,,0,0,0,,And this is gonna carry you very far, um...\N{\rChinese}这将把你们带得很远，嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.86,1:08:42.22,English,,0,0,0,,in life, okay?\N{\rChinese}在生活里，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.52,1:08:44.50,English,,0,0,0,,So, um...\N{\rChinese}所以，嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.50,1:08:46.20,English,,0,0,0,,The course is...\N{\rChinese}这门课是……
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.62,1:08:50.52,English,,0,0,0,,Um... Has come to an end.\N{\rChinese}嗯……已经结束。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.88,1:08:53.38,English,,0,0,0,,And I will share with you\N{\rChinese}我会与大家分享
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.88,1:08:57.34,English,,0,0,0,,um... Why I teach this course, okay?\N{\rChinese}嗯……我为什么开这门课，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.34,1:09:00.88,English,,0,0,0,,Because... Some of you know,\N{\rChinese}因为……你们中有些人知道，
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.12,1:09:04.76,English,,0,0,0,,I do have a very prestigious education background,\N{\rChinese}我确实拥有非常有名望的教育背景，
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.90,1:09:07.70,English,,0,0,0,,as well as a career background,\N{\rChinese}以及职业背景。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.08,1:09:09.68,English,,0,0,0,,okay? And...\N{\rChinese}好吧？然后……
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.64,1:09:13.20,English,,0,0,0,,I could have been, what, a lawyer, I think?\N{\rChinese}我本来可以是个律师，应该是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.30,1:09:14.88,English,,0,0,0,,A lawyer. A rich lawyer.\N{\rChinese}一个律师。一个富有的律师。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.18,1:09:16.80,English,,0,0,0,,A professor, okay?\N{\rChinese}一名教授，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.92,1:09:20.22,English,,0,0,0,,But instead, I'm teaching high school in China.\N{\rChinese}但我在中国教高中。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.82,1:09:22.48,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Why am I doing this?\N{\rChinese}对吗？我为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.70,1:09:27.68,English,,0,0,0,,It's because... Um...\N{\rChinese}因为……呃……
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.90,1:09:31.22,English,,0,0,0,,I have three kids.\N{\rChinese}我有三个孩子。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.54,1:09:33.62,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? I have three young kids.\N{\rChinese}好的？我有三个小孩子。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.76,1:09:36.04,English,,0,0,0,,My eldest is six.\N{\rChinese}我的大儿子六岁。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.22,1:09:37.96,English,,0,0,0,,My youngest is only about eight months.\N{\rChinese}我的小儿子才八个月。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.20,1:09:40.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And as a father,\N{\rChinese}我作为父亲，
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.66,1:09:45.22,English,,0,0,0,,you have to believe in a better world.\N{\rChinese}你要相信更好的世界。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.94,1:09:49.52,English,,0,0,0,,But not only do you have to believe in a better world, you have to imagine.\N{\rChinese}但你不仅要相信更好的世界，还要去想象。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.84,1:09:51.16,English,,0,0,0,,You have to fight for it.\N{\rChinese}你要为之而战。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.86,1:09:53.82,English,,0,0,0,,Because... Um...\N{\rChinese}因为……呃……
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.82,1:09:58.50,English,,0,0,0,,You have to leave behind a legacy for your children.\N{\rChinese}你要为孩子们留下遗产。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.74,1:10:00.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So,\N{\rChinese}好的？所以，
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.46,1:10:06.12,English,,0,0,0,,why I teach this course is to bring you a message of hope.\N{\rChinese}我开这门课的原因是给你们送去一份希望的讯息。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.28,1:10:08.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Like, through your own imagination,\N{\rChinese}好吧？就是通过自己的想象，
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.26,1:10:12.40,English,,0,0,0,,through your own hard work, you can create a better world.\N{\rChinese}通过自己的努力，你们就能创造更好的世界。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.94,1:10:15.62,English,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sit back and just let the world happen.\N{\rChinese}你不必坐着等着世界发生。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.10,1:10:17.50,English,,0,0,0,,You don't have to wait for the future.\N{\rChinese}你不必等待未来。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.62,1:10:20.06,English,,0,0,0,,You can make it happen. And...\N{\rChinese}你可以让它发生。并且……
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.72,1:10:22.62,English,,0,0,0,,If you really...\N{\rChinese}如果你真的……
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.26,1:10:27.58,English,,0,0,0,,work hard at it, you can make the world a better place.\N{\rChinese}努力去做，你就能让世界变得更好。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.80,1:10:29.30,English,,0,0,0,,And I think, like, this year\N{\rChinese}我想，这一年……
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.88,1:10:31.34,English,,0,0,0,,has proven to me\N{\rChinese}已向我证明
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.62,1:10:34.92,English,,0,0,0,,that I can make the world a better place\N{\rChinese}我可以让世界变得更好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.82,1:10:39.78,English,,0,0,0,,if I work hard. Because I've seen the growth in all of you.\N{\rChinese}只要我努力
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.06,1:10:43.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, I hope we can stay in touch.\N{\rChinese}好的？所以，我希望我们能保持联系。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.08,1:10:45.58,English,,0,0,0,,I hope that...\N{\rChinese}我希望……
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.06,1:10:49.12,English,,0,0,0,,Um... You will tell me how you progress, because\N{\rChinese}嗯……你会告诉我你的进展。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.12,1:10:52.60,English,,0,0,0,,I'm very confident that all of you will do very well in university.\N{\rChinese}我很有信心，你们在大学里会表现得很出色。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.62,1:10:55.88,English,,0,0,0,,And in life. And maybe at some point,\N{\rChinese}在生活中也是如此。也许在某个时刻，
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.64,1:11:01.70,English,,0,0,0,,we can share this dream of psychohistory.\N{\rChinese}我们可以共享这份关于心理史的梦想。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.84,1:11:06.34,English,,0,0,0,,You know? I know it sounds very complicated.\N{\rChinese}你知道吗？我知道听起来很复杂。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.58,1:11:09.14,English,,0,0,0,,It's very abstract. But\N{\rChinese}很抽象。但
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.14,1:11:13.38,English,,0,0,0,,to make this work, you need a lot of people working together.\N{\rChinese}要把这件事做成，得有很多人一起合作。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.74,1:11:16.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And it's something that's not going to happen tomorrow.\N{\rChinese}好的？这件事不是明天就能完成的。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.28,1:11:21.14,English,,0,0,0,,But it's something that we might come back to later on in our lives.\N{\rChinese}但它是我们以后生活中可能会再次回到的事。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.96,1:11:23.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, that's it.\N{\rChinese}好的？好了，就是这样。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.20,1:11:26.98,English,,0,0,0,,Thank you. And we'll stay in touch.\N{\rChinese}谢谢。我们会保持联系。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.02,1:11:30.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Subtitles by the Amara.org community\N{\rChinese}好的？字幕由Amara.org社区制作。
